20in%20jeans%20and%20their%20preferred%20team%20jersey%20(both%20of%20which%20are%20banned%20during%20a%20typical%20EBC%20pool%20party).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20a%20few%20groups%20who%20brought%20out%20their%20sparkly%20Vegas%20best%2C%20but%20most%20people%20opted%20for%20comfort.%20Even%20Gronk%20stayed%20in%20his%20sweatshirt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20club's%20pools%20were%20empty%20throughout%20the%20day%2C%20despite%20being%20heated.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gronk%20Beach%202024%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ca6ac094aa8ee8e84a38fc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOne%20of%20the%20pools%20at%20Encore%20Beach%20Club%20during%20Gronk%20Beach%202024.%20%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20time%20I%20saw%20someone%20enter%20one%20of%20the%20pools%20was%20when%20a%20man%20in%20jeans%20ran%20in%2C%20ankle-deep%2C%20to%20catch%20a%20flying%20football.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBut%20the%20casino%20pit%20at%20the%20bar%20was%20packed.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gronk%20Beach%202024%20bar%20area%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ca6a976fcb546d2d4e9dee%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPeople%20gambling%20at%20Gronk%20Beach%202024.%20%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEBC's%20craps%20and%20blackjack%20tables%20were%20brimming%20with%20energy%20as%20people%20yelped%20with%20joy%20over%20their%20wins%20throughout%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20made%20my%20way%20to%20the%20main%20bar%2C%20where%20I%20was%20greeted%20with%20a%20giant%20shirtless%20painting%20of%20Gronk.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gronk%20Beach%202024%20bar%5C%22%20char