a%20hot%20version%20of%20the%20Hazelnut%20Heartthrob%20coffee%20and%20two%20food%20items%3A%20the%20Everything%20Encore%20Breakfast%20Sandwich%20and%20an%20assortment%20of%20three%20DunKings%20Munchkins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Munchkins%20come%20on%20a%20skewer%2C%20resembling%20%26quot%3Bthe%20olive%20in%20a%20martini%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20chain's%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ordered%20the%20entire%20menu%20in%20NYC%2C%20which%20totaled%20%2417.37%2C%20and%20ranked%20each%20item%20from%20worst%20to%20best.%20Take%20a%20look.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E6.%20The%20Mixed%20Berry%20Beats%20Dunkin'%20Refresher%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Mixed%20Berry%20Beats%20Dunkin'%20Refresher.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ca64bc94aa8ee8e84a35e7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221707%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Mixed%20Berry%20Beats%20Dunkin'%20Refresher.%3Cp%3EMaria%20Noyen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20small%20version%20of%20the%20Mixed%20Berry%20Beats%20Dunkin'%20Refresher%20costs%20%242.79.%20The%20drink%20is%20flavored%20with%20strawberry%20dragonfruit%2C%20green%20tea%2C%20and%20an%20extra%20raspberry-flavored%20syrup%20shot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20taking%20my%20first%20sip%2C%20I%20could%20tell%20the%20beverage%20would%20contain%20bold%20flavorings%20from%20its%20distinct%20red%20color.%20I%20wasn't%20wrong.%20The%20drink%20had%20a%20very%20strong%20artificial%20fruit%20taste%20that%20was%20too%20overwhelming%2C%20in%20my%20opinion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithout%20the%20extra%20shot%20of%20raspberry%20syrup%2C%20it%20would've%20been%20a%20lot%20more%20palatable%20and%20refreshing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E5.%20The%20Everything%20Encore%20Breakfast%20Sandwich%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20breakfast%20sandwich.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ca65436e2e190e71a39bc7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20breakfast%20sandwich.%3Cp%3EMaria%20Noyen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20%244.29%2C%20the%20breakfast%20sandwich%20is%20the%20priciest%20item%20on%20the%20%26quot%3BDunKings%26quot%3B%20menu.%20The%20ingredients%20include%20sweet%20black%20pepper%20seasoned%20bacon%2C%20white%20cheddar%20cheese%2C%20and%20an%20egg%20sandwiched%20between%20an%20everything%20bagel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20first%20issue%20with%20the%20sandwich%20is%20that%20my%20order%20didn't%20come%20in%20an%20everything%20bagel%20but%20a%20plain%20one.%20Besides%20that%2C%20I%20couldn't%20taste%20much%20flavor%20or%20sharpness%20in%20the%20cheddar%20cheese.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20bacon%20was%20well-seasoned%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0a%20perfect%20blend%20of%20sweetness%20and%20saltiness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20overall%2C%20I%20found%20the%20sandwich%20to%20be%20a%20bit%20dry%20and%20think%20a%20sauce%20could've%20fixed%20that%20problem%20while%20adding%20some%20much-needed%20flavor.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E4.%20The%20Hazelnut%20Heartthrob%20Iced%20Coffee%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Hazelnut%20Heartthrob%20Iced%20Coffee.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ca664394aa8ee8e84a3694%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221707%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Hazelnut%20Heartthrob%20Iced%20Coffee.%3Cp%3EMaria%20Noyen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Hazelnut%20Heartthrob%20is%20the%20second-cheapest%20beverage%20on%20the%20menu.%20A%20small%20version%20of%20the%20drink%2C%20which%20contains%20Dunkin'%20Donuts'%20original%20blend%20of%20coffee%2C%20whole%20milk%2C%20two%20pumps%20of%20Hazelnut%20syrup%2C%20and%20two%20pumps%20of%20Caramel%20Swirl%20syrup%2C%20costs%20%242.59.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20the%20refresher%2C%20I%20found%20the%20iced%20version%20of%20the%20Hazelnut%20Heartthrob%20overpoweringly%20sweet%20from%20the%20syrups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20flavor%20improved%20slightly%20when%20I%20stirred%20the%20drink%20with%20a%20straw%20to%20mix%20the%20syrup%20collected%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20cup%20with%20the%20milk%2C%20but%20it%20wasn't%20enough%20to%20rank%20higher%20in%20my%20menu%20review.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E3.%20The%20Hazelnut%20Heartthrob%20Coffee%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Hazelnut%20Heartthrob%20Coffee.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ca679894aa8ee8e84a379a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221707%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Hazelnut%20Heartthrob%20Coffee.%3Cp%3EMaria%20Noyen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hot%20Hazelnut%20Heartthrob%20coffee%20isn't%20just%20a%20better%20deal%20than%20the%20iced%20version%3B%20it%20tastes%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20%241.99%2C%20the%20small%20coffee%20had%20all%20the%20same%20ingredients%20as%20the%20iced%20version%2C%20but%20I%20found%20that%20the%20syrups%20didn't%20separate%20from%20the%20milk%20as%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20ingredients%20blended%20so%20that%20each%20sip%20had%20the%20perfect%20milk-to-syrup%20ratio%2C%20making%20it%20far%20less%20sweet%20and%20easier%20to%20drink%20than%20the%20iced%20version.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E2.%20The%20DunKings%20Munchkins%20Skewer%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20DunKings%20Munchkins%20Skewer.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ca65d66e2e190e71a39bf9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221707%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20DunKings%20Munchkins%20Skewer.%3Cp%3EMaria%20Noyen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20DunKings%20Munchkins%20Skewer%20was%20my%20favorite%20food%20item%2C%20and%20at%20%241%2C%20it's%20also%20the%20cheapest%20item%20on%20the%20entire%20menu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20consists%20of%20three%20different%20flavored%20mini%20doughnuts%20held%20together%20through%20an%20orange%20skewer.%20The%20flavors%20I%20got%20were%20classic%20glazed%2C%20chocolate%20glazed%2C%20and%20one%20that%20tasted%20as%20if%20it%20was%20spiced%20with%20cinnamon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20I%20found%20the%20skewer%20unnecessary%20as%20the%20mini%20doughnuts%20fell%20off%20after%20one%20bite%2C%20and%20I%20didn't%20see%20the%20point%20in%20sticking%20the%20skewer%20into%20any%20of%20the%20drinks%20I%20ordered%2C%20I%20loved%20how%20light%20the%20texture%20of%20each%20little%20ball%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20all%20had%20a%20crispy%2C%20glazed%2C%20iced%20exterior%20but%20were%20perfectly%20fluffy%20and%20a%20good%20portioned%20snack%20to%20have%20along%20with%20a%20coffee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E1.%20The%20DunKings%20Iced%20Coffee%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20DunKings%20Iced%20Coffee.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ca673c6e2e190e71a39cc7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221707%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20DunKings%20Iced%20Coffee.%3Cp%3EThe%20DunKings%20Iced%20Coffee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Dunkin'%20Donuts%2C%20the%20DunKings%20Iced%20Coffee%20is%20Affleck's%20go-to%20drink%20order.%20After%20trying%20it%20myself%2C%20I%20get%20why.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20%243.29%2C%20it's%20the%20most%20expensive%20drink%20on%20the%20menu%2C%20but%20it's%20worth%20it%2C%20especially%20if%20you%20have%20a%20sweet%20tooth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20beverage%20features%20unsweetened%20vanilla%20flavoring%2C%20french%20vanilla%20swirl%20syrup%2C%20cream%2C%20sweet%20cold%20foam%2C%20cinnamon%20sugar%2C%20and%20regular%20whole%20milk.%20The%20cinnamon%20sugar%20added%20a%20much-needed%20twist%20to%20the%20vanilla-heavy%20drink.%20Even%20though%20it%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20syrup%2C%20it%20blended%20