n%20body%20and%20add%20some%20accessory%20holders%20to%20the%20side%20of%20the%20charging%20base.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20immediately%20noticed%20how%20the%20design%20of%20the%20Tineco%20Floor%20One%20S7%20Pro%20differed%20from%20the%20Tineco%20Floor%20One%20S5%20version%20I%20previously%20tested.%20For%20one%2C%20the%20wheels%20of%20the%20S7%20Pro%20were%20larger%20and%20covered%20in%20thick%20rubber%20and%20deep%20grooves.%20They%20glided%20more%20softly%20on%20my%20hardwood%20floor%2C%20especially%20over%20my%20considerably%20tall%20thresholds.%20The%20body%20of%20the%20wet-dry%20vacuum%2C%20which%20was%20made%20with%20thick%20plastic%2C%20now%20mimicked%20wood%20panel%20grains%2C%20adding%20to%20the%20sleeker%20style.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20vacuum%20head%20of%20the%20S5%20was%20designed%20so%20that%20only%20a%20close-edge%20cleaning%20could%20occur%20on%20the%20right%20side%20of%20the%20vacuum%20head%2C%20as%20there%20is%20an%20inch-thick%20plastic%20piece%20on%20the%20left%20side%20of%20the%20brush%20roll.%20With%20the%20Tineco%20Floor%20One%20S7%20Pro%2C%20the%20floorhead%20enables%20close-edge%20cleaning%20on%20either%20side%2C%20within%20one%20centimeter%20of%20the%20wall.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Our%20review%20of%20the%20Tineco%20Floor%20One%20S7%20Pro%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOur%20review%20of%20the%20Tineco%20Floor%20One%20S7%20Pro%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tested%20the%20Tineco%20Floor%20One%20S7%20Pro%20vacuum%20over%20two%20months%20in%20my%201%2C600-square-foot%20home.%20With%20laminate%20and%20historic%20hardwood%20floors%20that%20get%20particularly%20dusty%2C%20there%20were%20many%20opportunities%20to%20test%20the%20S7%20Pro's%20cleaning%20capabilities.%20Because%20of%20the%20wet-dry%20vacuum's%20design%2C%20my%20floors%20are%20far%20cleaner%20than%20they%20were%20before%20I%20started%20using%20this%20machine%20at%20least%20once%20a%20week.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EOverall%20Ease%20of%20Use%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Tineco%20Floor%20One%20S7%20Pro%20%20being%20used%20on%20a%20hardwood%20floor%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65afdc4f43bb77284b9fb40f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Tineco%20Pure%20One%20S7%20Pro%20has%20a%20vivid%20LCD%20interface%20with%20a%20cleaning%20assistance%20and%20dirt%20detection%20tech%20that%20indicates%20how%20dirty%20floors%20are.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Temblador%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20this%20is%20a%20relatively%20easy%20wet-dry%20vacuum%20to%20use%20and%20has%20a%20lot%20to%20do%20with%20the%203.6-inch%20LCD%20screen%2C%20unlike%20anything%20I've%20seen%20on%20any%20other%20wet-dry%20vacuum.%20Upon%20turning%20on%20the%20wet-dry%20vacuum%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20an%20interactive%20tutorial%20guide%20with%20a%20Tineco%20Assistant%20that%20looks%20like%20a%20colorful%203D%20cartoon%20played%20on%20the%20LCD%20screen%20guiding%20me%20through%20the%20set-up%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20LCD%20screen%20provides%20visual%20cues%20as%20you%20clean%20and%20undergo%20the%20self-cleaning%20maintenance.%20Everything%20from%20the%20mode%20that%20is%20currently%20in%20use%20to%20the%20battery%20life%20and%20the%20clean%20water%20tank%20levels%20are%20displayed%20on%20the%20screen.%20The%20assistant%20occasionally%20provides%20verbal%20instructions%20such%20as%20%26quot%3Brefill%20the%20clean%20water%20tank%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bplace%20the%20wet-dry%20vacuum%20on%20the%20charger%26quot%3B%20when%20the%20battery%20is%20low.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222534%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20tineco%20cleans%20on%20hard%20floor%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ca5af66fcb546d2d4e93bf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20%26quot%3BiLoop%20smart%20sensor%26quot%3B%20turns%20red%20when%20the%20system%20recognizes%20dirt%2C%20debris%2C%20or%20a%20stain%20and%20changes%20to%20blue%20as%20the%20area%20becomes%20clean.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Temblador%2F%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20a%20headlight%20turns%20on%20when%20the%20wet-dry%20vacuum%20powers%20up%2C%20allowing%20you%20to%20see%20dust%20and%20debris%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20the%20iLoop%20Smart%20Sensor%20encircles%20the%20LCD%20screen%20that%20indicates%20to%20you%20if%20your%20floors%20are%20dirty%20or%20clean.%20This%20%26quot%3Bloop%26quot%3B%20turns%20red%20when%20the%20smart%20system%20recognizes%20the%20floor%20has%20dirt%2C%20debris%2C%20or%20a%20stain.%20That%20loop%20slowly%20changes%20to%20the%20color%20blue%20as%20you%20vacuum%20and%20mop%20over%20the%20dirty%20area.%20When%20the%20loop%20is%20completely%20blue%2C%20the%20floor%20is%20clean.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20ergonomic%20handle%2C%20you'll%20find%20the%20self-cleaning%20button%20on%20top%20and%20a%20power%20button%20in%20the%20front.%20Above%20the%20power%20button%20is%20a%20four-direction%20button%20used%20to%20move%20through%20the%20different%20cleaning%20modes%C2%A0on%20the%20LCD%20screen%20and%20the%20settings%20button.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%2011.31%20lbs.%2C%20this%20wet-dry%20vacuum%20isn't%20the%20lightest%20I've%20tested%2C%20but%20thanks%20to%20a%20self-propulsion%20system%2C%20it%20glides%20forward%20and%20backward%20easily.%20My%20arm%20never%20once%20tired.%20The%20self-propulsion%20system%2C%20combined%20with%20the%20wet-dry%20vacuum%20head's%20swivel%20ability%2C%20allows%20it%20to%20reach%20difficult%20places%20and%20around%20objects%20without%20moving%20them.%20The%20vacuum%20head%20is%20not%20too%20tall%20or%20wide%20so%20that%20it%20can%20fit%20under%20cabinets%20and%20in%20tight%20spaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20appreciate%20that%20the%20vacuum%20pauses%20when%20standing%20upright%20and%20that%20the%20Tineco%20Floor%20One%20S7%20Pro%20can%20lean%20back%20about%2030%20degrees%20so%20that%20I%20can%20reach%20further%20under%20beds%2C%20dressers%2C%20and%20the%20like.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3ECleaning%20Performance%C2%A0%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Tineco%20cleans%20mustard%20on%20hard%20floor%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ca4c336fcb546d2d4e8b3b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Tineco%20can%20clean%20up%20dry%20debris%20like%20flour%2C%20coffee%20and%20Cheerios%20as%20well%20as%20liquids%20like%20syrup%2C%20juice%2C%20and%20barbecue%20sauce%20in%20a%20single%20pass.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Temblador%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20wet-dry%20vacuum%20has%20four%20different%20modes%20%E2%80%93%20auto%2C%20max%2C%20ultra%2C%20and%20suction.%20Max%20is%20essentially%20a%20deeper%20clean%20than%20auto%20mode%2C%20while%20ultra%20is%20best%20used%20when%20you%20want%20to%20better%20utilize%20the%20Tineco%20cleaning%20solution%20to%20sanitize%20your%20floors.%20The%20suction%20mode%20suctions%20up%20excess%20liquid%20and%20spills.%20In%20terms%20of%20noise%2C%20the%20wet-dry%20vacuum%20emits%20a%20sound%20rating%20of%2070%20decibels%20in%20auto%20mode%2C%2073%20in%20max%20mode%2C%2071%20in%20ultra%20mode%2C%20and%2075%20in%20suction%20mode.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20users%20will%20get%20by%20with%20Auto-mode%2C%20which%20does%20a%20phenomenal%20job%20cleaning%20floors.%20The%20wet-dry%20vacuum%20cleaned%20fine%20materials%20like%20flour%20and%20coffee%2C%20large%20debris%20like%20Cheerios%2C%20and%20even%20liquids%20like%20syrup%2C%20juice%2C%20and%20barbecue%20sauce%20in%20a%20single%20pass.%20When%20it%20came%20to%20dried%20foods%2C%20liquids%2C%20or%20mud%2C%20it%20took%20anywhere%20from%20two%20to%20four%20passes%20of%20the%20S7%20Pro%2C%20depending%20on%20how%20caked%20it%20was%20to%20the%20floor.%20It's%20best%20to%20increase%20the%20mode%20to%20max%20or%20ultra%20on%20stickier%20stains%2C%20even%20though%20auto%20mode%20does%20a%20decent%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20vacuuming%2C%20the%20Tineco%20Floor%20One%20S7%20Pro%20increases%20suction%20when%20the%20smart%20system%20recognizes%20a%20dirty%20floor.%20I%20was%20equally%20happy%20with%20how%20the%20S7%20Pro%20doesn't%20leave%20a%20lot%20of%20standing%20water.%20This%20is%20always%20a%20concern%20as%20I%20have%20103-year-old%20wooden%20floors%2C%20and%20too%20much%20water%20can%20damage%20such%20flooring.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I'm%20moving%20the%20wet-dry%20vacuum%20across%20my%20floors%2C%20the%20machine%20continually%20flushes%20clean%20water%20through%20the%20brush%20roll%20so%20that%20it%20remains%20fairly%20clean%20and%20I'm%20not%20pushing%20dirt%20and%20grime%20from%20one%20spot%20to%20the%20next.%20There%20is%20also%20a%20scraper%20that%20essentially%20%26quot%3Bwrings%26quot%3B%20the%20dirty%20water%20from%20the%20brush%20roll%2C%20which%20is%20immediately%20suctioned%20into%20the%20dirty%20water%20tank.%20You%20can't%20get%20this%20kind%20of%20cleaning%20assurance%20with%20a%20mop%20or%20even%20a%20robot%20vacuum%20with%20mopping%20and%20vacuuming%20capabilities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22the%20tineco%20cleans%20along%20the%20edge%20of%20a%20wall%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ca596394aa8ee8e84a2d9c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20floorhead%20enables%20close-edge%20cleaning%20on%20either%20side%2C%20within%20one%20centimeter%20of%20the%20wall.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Temblador%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Tineco%20Floor%20One%20S7%20Pro%20picks%20up%20debris%20and%20dirt%20as%20well%20forward%20as%20it%20does%20backward%2C%20which%20is%20not%20the%20case%20for%20all%20wet-dry%20vacuums.%20The%20brush%20roll%20can%20reach%20within%20one%20centimeter%20of%20the%20wall%20on%20either%20side%20of%20the%20vacuum%20head.%20In%20fact%2C%20it's%20better%20to%20use%20the%20edge%20rather%20than%20the%20front%20of%20the%20vacuum%20head%20to%20clean%20along%20a%20wall%2C%20as%20the%20front%20of%20the%20vacuum%20head%20can%20only%20reach%20within%20about%203%2F4ths%20of%20an%20inch.%20(For%20reference%2C%20I've%20only%20seen%20one%20or%20two%20wet-dry%20vacuums%20with%20better%20cleaning%20along%20the%20front%20of%20the%20vacuum%20head.)%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EBattery%20life%C2%A0%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Tineco%2C%20this%20cordless%20wet-dry%20vacuum%20has%20a%20battery%20life%20of%20up%20to%2040%20minutes.%20During%20my%20testing%2C%20the%20battery%20had%2010%20percent%20of%20charge%20remaining%20after%2043%20minutes%20of%20use.%20I%20probably%20could%20have%20cleaned%20the%20floors%20for%20another%20five%20minutes%20(at%20most)%20before%20it%20died%20completely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20battery%20that%20can%20last%20over%2040%20minutes%20is%20way%20more%20than%20I%20need%20to%20clean%20my%201%2C600-square-foot%20house.%20The%20battery%20doesn't%20even%20get%20to%2050%20percent%20by%20the%20time%20I'm%20done%20cleaning%20on%20auto%20mode.%20When%20I%20used%20the%20wet-dry%20vacuum%20on%20Ultra%20and%20Max%20mode%2C%20the%20battery%20was%20at%2047%20percent%20when%20I%20was%20done.%20Most%20people%20will%20likely%20be%20able%20to%20clean%20their%20entire%20home%20without%20needing%20to%20pause%20to%20charge%20the%20wet-dry%20vacuum.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EMaintenance%20and%20cleaning%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22LCD%20screen%20shows%20cleaning%20progress%20on%20the%20Tineco%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ca4c72917a1dae024588ce%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20LCD%20assistant%20displays%20what's%20happening%20during%20the%20self-cleaning%20cycle%20with%20notifications%20like%20soaking%20the%20brush%20roller%2C%20cleaning%20the%20brush%20roller%2C%20cleaning%20the%20pipes%20and%20deep%20cleaning.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Temblador%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3EThe%20maintenance%20and%20self-cleaning%20process%20for%20the%20Tineco%20Floor%20One%20S7%20Pro%20is%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20hassle%2C%20but%20not%20more%20so%20than%20any%20other%20wet-dry%20vacuum%20with%20a%20similar%20design%20on%20the%20market.%20When%20I'm%20finished%20vacuuming%20and%20mopping%20the%20house%20with%20the%20S7%20Pro%2C%20I%20place%20it%20on%20the%20charger%20and%20hit%20the%20self-cleaning%20button%20on%20the%20top%20of%20the%20handle.%20Two%20options%20appear%20on%20the%20LCD%20screen%3A%20Quick%20self-cleaning%2C%20which%20requires%202%20minutes%2C%20and%20a%20Super%20self-cleaning%20option%2C%20which%20requires%206%20minutes.%3Cp%3EThe%20Super%20self-cleaning%20mode%20does%20a%20better%20job%20of%20flushing%20out%20dust%2C%20debris%2C%20and%20hair%20from%20the%20brush%20roll%20and%20the%20vacuum%20head.%20It's%20not%20perfect%20by%20any%20means%2C%20but%20it%20results%20in%20less%20cleanup%20on%20my%20part.%20The%20self-cleaning%20process%20has%20a%20sound%20rating%20between%2065-77%20decibels.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%C2%A0%20LCD%20screen%20depicts%20the%20self-cleaning%20process%20as%20it%20happens%2C%20starting%20with%20the%20Tineco%20soaking%20the%20brush%20roller%20and%20then%20cleaning%20it%20before%20flushing%20water%20through%20the%20main%20pipe.%20From%20there%2C%20the%20brush%20roller%20undergoes%20a%20deep%20cleaning%20before%20it%20is%20air-dried.%20The%20air-drying%20process%20lasts%20for%20one%20minute%20during%20the%20Quick%20self-cleaning%20and%20about%204.5%20minutes%20during%20the%20Super%20self-cleaning%20process.%20As%20the%20brush%20roll%20rotates%2C%20air%20is%20pulled%20through%20the%20vacuum%20head.%20However%2C%20it's%20not%20enough%20time%20to%20fully%20dry%20the%20brush%20roll.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20self-cleaning%20process%20is%20completed%2C%20I%20remove%20the%20dirty%20water%20tank%20and%20dispose%20of%20the%20dirty%20water%2C%20but%20not%20before%20I%20try%20to%20remove%20hair%20and%20debris%20with%20the%20brush%20provided.%20The%20cleaning%20brush%20is%20now%20a%20malleable%20wire%20brush%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20small%20soft%20bristles%20that%20can%20better%20grab%20onto%20hair%20and%20debris%20in%20the%20dirty%20water%20tank.%20I%20used%20to%20pour%20the%20dirty%20water%20tank%20into%20my%20sink%20and%20turn%20on%20the%20disposal%20afterward.%20Still%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20this%20is%20the%20best%20course%20because%20some%20hair%20and%20debris%20will%20inevitably%20make%20their%20way%20to%20my%20disposal%2C%20and%20I'm%20nervous%20that%20it%20will%20affect%20it%20over%20time.%20Now%2C%20I%20empty%20the%20dirty%20water%20tank%20outside%2C%20but%20the%20toilet%20is%20an%20option%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20emptied%2C%20I%20thoroughly%20clean%20the%20dirty%20water%20tank%2C%20which%20can%20cause%20an%20awful%20smell%20if%20not%20cleaned%20well%20and%20allowed%20to%20dry.%20To%20clean%20the%20dirty%20water%20tank%2C%20I%20must%20also%20rinse%20the%20air%20filter%20at%20the%20same%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tineco%20floorhead%20close%20up%20for%20cleaning%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ca59f56fcb546d2d4e9330%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Tineco%20Floor%20One%20S7%20Pro%20does%20require%20extra%20attention%20beyond%20the%20self-cleaning%20mode.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Temblador%2F%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3EThe%20final%20step%20is%20to%20remove%20the%20vacuum%20head%20and%20clean%20bits%20of%20dust%20and%20debris%20stuck%20on%20the%20cover%20with%20a%20paper%20towel.%20I'll%20then%20remove%20the%20brush%20roll%20so%20it%20can%20air%20dry%20and%20clean%20off%20any%20dust%20and%20debris%20that%20wasn't%20flushed%20out%20through%20the%20self-cleaning%20process.%20After%20that%2C%20I'll%20replace%20the%20brush%20roll%20with%20the%20additional%20dry%20brush%20roll%20provided.%3Cp%3EThe%20maintenance%20and%20clean-up%20may%20seem%20like%20a%20lot%20of%20work%2C%20but%20once%20you've%20done%20it%20a%20few%20times%2C%20the%20process%20goes%20quickly.%20It's%20imperative%20that%20you%20clean%20out%20all%20the%20nooks%20and%20crannies%20of%20the%20machine%20so%20you%20don't%20continue%20to%20clean%20with%20dirt%20and%20dust%20trapped%20in%20the%20vacuum%20head.%20Unfortunately%2C%20I%20have%20not%20found%20a%20wet-dry%20vacuum%20with%20a%20similar%20design%20that%20offers%20a%20completely%20hands-off%20self-cleaning%20system.%20That%20said%2C%20I'm%20willing%20to%20put%20in%20the%20small%20amount%20of%20work%20necessary%20to%20ensure%20my%20floors%20are%20incredibly%20clean.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EFiltration%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ETineco%20Floor%20One%20S7%20Pro%20is%20outfitted%20with%20what%20Tineco%20calls%20a%20%26quot%3Bdry%20filter.%26quot%3B%20It%20traps%20foam%20and%20small%20bits%20of%20debris%2C%20like%20hair%20or%20leaves.%20The%20filter%20should%20be%20removed%20during%20the%20maintenance%20and%20cleaning%20steps%20of%20the%20dirty%20water%20tank%20and%20cleaned%20thoroughly%20with%20water.%20I%20then%20let%20it%20air%20dry%20for%20at%20least%20a%20day.%20Since%20Tineco%20provides%20two%20air%20filters%2C%20I%20switch%20to%20a%20dry%20one%20after%20each%20cleaning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20other%20type%20of%20filtration%20system%20for%20the%20Tineco%20Floor%20One%20S7%20Pro%2C%20which%20is%20unfortunate.%20I%20would%20have%20liked%20the%20dirty%20water%20tank%20to%20have%20a%20pet%20hair%20or%20debris%20filter%20so%20that%20I%20could%20more%20easily%20remove%20debris%20from%20the%20dirty%20water%20before%20disposing%20of%20it.%20In%20the%20future%2C%20I'd%20like%20to%20see%20Tineco%20design%20a%20wet-dry%20vacuum%20with%20a%20small%20trash%20bin%20so%20that%20there%20was%20even%20less%20debris%20in%20the%20dirty%20water%20tank.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Cons%20to%20consider%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%20to%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20consider%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20live%20in%20a%20house%20with%20all%20hard%20floors%2C%20it's%20likely%20that%20you'll%20have%20an%20area%20rug%20or%20two%2C%20like%20I%20do.%20Yes%2C%20I%20keep%20it%20thoroughly%20vacuumed%2C%20but%20it%20would%20be%20nice%20to%20have%20one%20product%20that%20could%20clean%20the%20hard%20floors%20and%20the%20rugs%20during%20the%20same%20cleaning%20session.%20I'm%20surprised%20that%20the%20Tineco%20Floor%20One%20S7%20Pro%20does%20not%20have%20the%20capability%20to%20also%20clean%20rugs%2C%20especially%20when%20you%20consider%20that%20there%20are%20more%20affordable%20wet-dry%20vacuums%20on%20the%20market%2C%20like%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-63870-20%26h%3D03e1b4ceec0bc76d70078a7fcc504b666196f588d59647cc7b50117ef2a4db2d%26postID%3D65ca3f9db1a0a2d0772a04bb%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Ftineco-floor-one-s7-pro-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.walmart.com%252Fip%252FEcowell-LULU-Quick-Clean-P05-Cordless-Multi-Surface-Wet-Dry-Vacuum%252F1086944929%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEcowell%20Lulu%20Quick%20Clean%20P05%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20that%20have%20this%20capability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20the%20very%20expensive%20price%2C%20the%20only%20other%20con%20to%20be%20mindful%20of%20is%20the%20maintenance%20required%20of%20the%20Tineco%20Floor%20One%20S7%20Pro.%20No%20matter%20the%20wet-dry%20vacuum%20(robots%20aside)%2C%20you're%20going%20to%20have%20to%20conduct%20the%20icky%20chore%20of%20emptying%20a%20dirty%20water%20tank%20and%20removing%20some%20dust%20and%20such%20around%20the%20brush%20roll%20in%20the%20vacuum%20head.%20With%20such%20a%20big%20price%20tag%2C%20it%20is%20unfortunate%20that%20the%20Tineco%20Floor%20One%20S7%20Pro%20doesn't%20have%20a%20heated%20drying%20system%20for%20the%20brush%