ifferent%20types%20of%20knives%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EDoesn't%20work%20well%20with%20small%20(paring)%20knives%20or%20scissors%2C%20not%20as%20fine%20as%20stones%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElectric%20sharpeners%20are%20the%20fastest%2C%20easiest%2C%20and%20most%20dependable%20tools%20for%20sharpening%20knives%2C%20and%20the%20Chef's%20Choice%20Trizor%20XV%20offers%20three%20different%20bevels%20of%2025%2C%2020%2C%20and%2015%20degrees%2C%20making%20it%20the%20best%20knife%20sharpener%20for%20most%20knives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20took%20the%20edge%20off%20of%20a%20Victorinox%20Fibrox%20Chef's%20Knife%20(the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fbest-knife-set%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20budget%20chef's%20knife%3C%2Fa%3E%20we%20tested)%20using%20concrete.%20After%20less%20than%20five%20minutes%20of%20running%20it%20through%20all%20three%20stages%20of%20the%20Trizor%20XV%2C%20it%20was%20shaving%20a%20path%20through%20the%20hair%20on%20the%20back%20of%20my%20hand%20%E2%80%94%20something%20it%20couldn't%20do%20right%20out%20of%20the%20box.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDifferent%20combinations%20of%20stages%20(follow%20instructions)%20offer%20different%20edges.%20In%20summary%2C%20running%20your%20knives%20through%20the%20third%20stage%20every%20few%20weeks%20will%20keep%20the%20blades%20fresh%20and%20extend%20the%20time%20between%20sharpening.%20If%20a%20knife%20is%20really%20dull%2C%20start%20with%20stage%20two%20(or%20one%20at%20worst).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20we%20like%20most%20about%20the%20Trizor%20XV%20(the%20%26quot%3BXV%26quot%3B%20refers%20to%20the%2015-degree%20sharpener)%20is%20the%20spring-loaded%20sharpening%20blades%20that%20grip%20the%20knife's%20edge%20at%20the%20correct%20angle%2C%20preventing%20you%20from%20damaging%20the%20blade%20as%20you%20pull%20it%20through.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.i