ives%2C%20doesn't%20make%20the%20finest%20edge%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20pull-through%20sharpener%20strikes%20a%20happy%20balance%20between%20quality%20and%20convenience.%20You're%20not%20going%20to%20get%20an%20edge%20that%20will%20appease%20a%20sushi%20chef%2C%20but%20you'll%20be%20able%20to%20slice%20tomatoes%20(or%20trim%20raw%20fish%20for%20that%20matter)%20with%20the%20end%20result.%20We%20tested%20seven%20pull-through%20sharpeners%20and%20found%20that%20M%C3%BCeller's%20Heavy-Duty%204-Stage%20Diamond%20Sharpener%20was%20the%20best%20knife%20sharpener%20in%20this%20style%20to%20turn%20out%20sharp%20edges%20with%20the%20least%20amount%20of%20difficulty.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20experts%20pointed%20us%20to%20three-stage%20sharpeners%2C%20and%20our%20testing%20confirmed%20that%20three%20stages%20seem%20to%20offer%20the%20best%20edge%20from%20a%20pull-through%2C%20but%20this%20model's%20fourth%20stage%2C%20for%20scissors%2C%20certainly%20doesn't%20hurt.%20Couple%20that%20with%20the%20fact%20that%20this%20sharpener%20is%20about%20the%20same%20price%20as%20less-intensive%20single-stage%20ones%2C%20and%20we%20had%20our%20pick.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20sharpened%20cheap%20drawer%20scissors%20and%20kitchen%20shears%2C%20as%20well%20as%20nearly-destroyed%20bait%20knives%20and%20fine%20German%20steel%20with%20this%20sharpener%20and%20while%20we%20didn't%20get%20a%20perfect%20edge%20on%20the%20latter%20two%20(that%20would%20be%20tough%20with%20most%20sharpeners)%2C%20we%20did%20get%20them%20serviceable%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20common%20issue%20we%20ran%20up%20against%20with%20pull-through%20sharpeners%20was%20getting%20a%20bite%20on%20edges%20without%20coarsely%20gouging%20away%20at%20them%2C%20which%20can%20be%20disastrous.%20With%20the%20exception%20of%20wider-angled%20pocket%20knife%20blades%2C%20everything%20ran%20through%20the%20M%C3%BCeller%20smoothly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20kit%3A%20Edge%20Pro%20Apex%202%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Edge%20Pro%20Apex%202%20sharpening%20a%20chef%E2%80%99s%20knife%20with%20three%20other%20knives%20on%20a%20granite%20countertop.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6169c62541af0d00193ee551%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWith%20this%20kit%2C%20we%20brought%20back%20everything%20from%20tortured%20bait%20knives%20to%20chipped%20carbon%20blades%20with%20little%20trouble%20at%20all.%3Cp%3EOwen%20Burke%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EDimensions%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E17.9%26quot%3BL%20x%205.4%26quot%3BW%20x%202.5%26quot%3BH%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EType%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EManual%20whetstones%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbrasive%20material%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ECeramic%20stones%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESharpens%20all%20knives%2C%20adjustable%20bevel%20settings%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESuction-cup%20grip%20doesn't%20work%20on%20all%20surfaces%2C%20best%20for%20kitchen%20knives%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20sharpening%20kit%2C%20specifically%20a%20jig%20system%20like%20Edge%20Pro's%20Apex%202%2C%20is%20a%20whetstone%20kit%20with%20training%20wheels.%20You%20get%20absolute%20control%20while%20using%20the%20most%20traditional%20sharpening%20tools%20(ceramic%20stones)%20without%20too%20much%20hassle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEdge%20Pro%20offers%20several%20different%20kits%2C%20but%20the%20Apex%202%20is%20a%20great%20place%20to%20start%20for%20just%20sharpening%20kitchen%20knives.%20You%20get%20three%20stones%20of%20220%2C%20400%2C%20and%20600%20grit%20ceramic%2C%20the%20kit%20itself%2C%20an%208%26quot%3B%20ceramic%20hone%2C%20a%20microfiber%20towel%2C%20a%20water%20bottle%20for%20careful%20dousing%2C%20and%20a%20black%20carrying%20case.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThanks%20to%20the%20marked%20angles%20on%20the%20vertical%20rod%20on%20which%20the%20jig%20pivots%2C%20we%20found%20the%20Apex%202%20exceptionally%20easy%20to%20set%20up%20and%20put%20to%20work.%20Start%20with%20a%20cheaper%20knife%20and%20use%20the%20instruction%20manual%3A%20it%20offers%20tips%20like%20how%20to%20find%20the%20edge%20of%20your%20blade%20by%20using%20a%20permanent%20marker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20thing%20we%20don't%20like%20about%20the%20Apex%20station%20is%20the%20suction%20cups%20that%20secure%20it.%20While%20they%20work%20extremely%20well%20on%20high-gloss%20surfaces%2C%20they%20wouldn't%20stick%20to%20my%20workbench.%20Since%20most%20people%20are%20sharpening%20in%20their%20kitchen%2C%20the%20suction%20cups%20should%20suffice%20for%20most.%20Ultimately%2C%20this%20kit%20will%20last%20decades%20and%20handle%20every%20kind%20of%20knife%20in%20your%20kitchen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20Edge%20Pro%20intimidates%20you%2C%20we%20suggest%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiipgf_060917_best-knife-sharpeners-20%26h%3D022deae6f9e1d4804a8b7f61a5db561144933f606f75f8375ba2afdff7dec196%26postID%3D61b8efc6f2a36b1ac9f41774%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fkitchen%252Fbest-knife-sharpener%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FOriginal-Tumbler-Rolling-Knife-SharpenerTM%252Fdp%252FB0CGGVHBQG%253Fth%253D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETumbler%20Rolling%20Knife%20Sharpener%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It's%20not%20as%20involved%20as%20the%20Apex%20and%20much%20simpler%20to%20use%2C%20but%20you'll%20get%20a%20feel%20for%20how%20the%20steel%20responds%20to%20different%20sharpening%20angles.%20We%20like%20it%20as%20a%20middle%20ground%20between%20a%20pull-through%20sharpener%20and%20a%20jig%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20compact%3A%20KitchenIQ%20Edge%20Grip%202-Stage%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20KitchenIQ%20Edge%20Grip%202-Stage%20sharpener%20on%20a%20granite%20countertop.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6169c72538c1960018302603%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOut%20of%20almost%20all%20of%20the%20smaller%20sharpeners%20we%20tested%2C%20this%20was%20by%20far%20the%20least%20likely%20to%20topple%20over.%3Cp%3EOwen%20Burke%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EDimensions%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E3.75%26quot%3BL%20x%202%26quot%3BW%20x%201.75%26quot%3BH%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EType%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EManual%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbrasive%20material%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ECarbide%20and%20ceramic%20rods%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESmall%2C%20stable%2C%20effective%20for%20basic%20sharpening%20and%20finishing%2C%20works%20on%20serrated%20blades%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EYou%20won't%20get%20as%20refined%20of%20an%20edge%20as%20with%20a%20three-stage%20sharpener%2C%20not%20good%20for%20scissors%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Kitchen%20IQ%202-Stage%20Knife%20Sharpener%20is%20almost%20as%20basic%20as%20knife%20sharpening%20gets%2C%20and%20if%20it's%20the%20difference%20between%20you%20owning%20a%20sharpener%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3Eany%20%3C%2Fem%3Esharpener%20%E2%80%94%20and%20not%2C%20spend%20the%20%2410%20and%20your%20knife%20work%20will%20become%20infinitely%20better%2C%20and%20perhaps%20more%20importantly%2C%20safer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20not%20much%20to%20the%20smallest%20of%20our%20best%20knife%20sharpener%20picks%3A%20the%20carbide%20blades%20make%20up%20the%20coarse%20treatment%20and%20the%20ceramic%20ones%20do%20the%20fine%20work%20to%20touch%20up%20the%20edge.%20What%20we%20like%20about%20it%20over%20the%20others%20in%20this%20size%20class%20is%20that%20it%20does%20have%20two%20stages%20as%20opposed%20to%20one%2C%20and%20it%20is%20incredibly%20stable%20with%20a%20low%20center%20of%20gravity%20and%20a%20comfortable%20grip.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDon't%20expect%20it%20to%20perform%20any%20miracle%20work%20on%20far-gone%20cutlery%2C%20but%20keeping%20it%20in%20regular%20use%20will%20keep%20the%20working%20knives%20you%20do%20have%20in%20commission%2C%20which%20is%20all%20most%20of%20us%20need%20anyhow.%20It's%20a%20great%20backup%20tool%20to%20have%20in%20your%20kitchen%2C%20and%20easy%20enough%20to%20pull%20out%20of%20the%20drawer%20and%20draw%20a%20knife%20or%20two%20through%20it%20a%20few%20times%20before%20prepping%20for%20dinner.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20compact%20sharpener%20worth%20a%20look%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiipgf_060917_best-knife-sharpeners-20%26h%3Db8c95659876fb2600ffe6eb63dc09401b512bc82bf4b9a37aaa1b7555843ed75%26postID%3D61b8efc6f2a36b1ac9f41774%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fkitchen%252Fbest-knife-sharpener%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FLansky-3289-P%252Fdp%252FB082VLPZ21%253Fth%253D1%2526psc%253D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELanksy%20D-Sharp%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20is%20a%20great%20pick%20for%20those%20sharpening%20on%20the%20go%20and%20keeping%20a%20variety%20of%20knives%20sharp.%20With%2017-%2C%2021-%2C%20and%2025-degree%20angles%20as%20well%20as%20a%20ceramic%20edge%20for%20honing%2C%20you%20can%20use%20this%20palm-sized%20sharpener%20with%20anything%20from%20a%20fillet%20knife%20to%20a%20pocket%20knife.%20This%20doesn't%20do%20the%20finest%20job%2C%20but%20it's%20versatile%2C%20extremely%20thin%20(about%20half%20an%20inch)%20and%20only%20a%20few%20inches%20long%2C%20so%20it'll%20fit%20in%20any%20kit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20a%20knife%20sharpener%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20consideration%20is%20the%20type%20of%20sharpener%2C%20whether%20that's%20manual%2C%20electric%2C%20pull%20through%2C%20or%20a%20stone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EManual%20vs%20electric%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EOur%20best%20knife%20sharpener%20overall%20is%20electric%2C%20which%20offers%20quicker%20and%20more%20consistent%20sharpening.%20However%2C%20our%20other%20three%20recommendations%20are%20manual%20sharpeners%20because%20not%20only%20did%20they%20perform%20comparably%20to%20the%20others%20we%20tested%2C%20but%20they%20also%20are%20cheaper%20and%20less%20bulky%20than%20electric%20ones.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPull%20through%20vs%20steel%20or%20stone%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWhile%20whetstones%20and%20grinding%20wheels%20reign%20supreme%2C%20we%20found%20through%20experience%20and%20interviews%20with%20experts%20above%20that%20they%20require%20a%20certain%20level%20of%20prowess%20most%20home%20cooks%20don't%20have.%20Further%20to%20that%20point%2C%20a%20grinding%20wheel%20is%20incredibly%20dangerous%20and%20has%20no%20place%20in%20most%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20really%20after%20a%20whetstone%2C%20the%20ones%20we%20recommend%20based%20on%20past%20testing%20are%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiipgf_060917_best-knife-sharpeners-20%26h%3Df3b8c2efdee70a21c39abef19b1b3986499a062b35a5815d9cdf46e1bbd623d3%26postID%3D61b8efc6f2a36b1ac9f41774%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fkitchen%252Fbest-knife-sharpener%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252Fdp%252FB00062BIT4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESmith's%20TRI-6%20Arkansas%20TRI-HOME%20Sharpening%20System%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20generally%2C%20we've%20found%20that%20electric%2C%20pull-through%2C%20kits%20(specifically%2C%20jig%20systems)%2C%20and%20portable%20options%20are%20best%20for%20most%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVersatility%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESome%20sharpeners%20%E2%80%94%20including%20most%20pull-through%20options%20%E2%80%94%20only%20offer%20a%20single%20setting.%20These%20work%20in%20a%20pinch%2C%20but%20we%20found%20that%20at%20least%20three%20options%20(one%20for%20coarse%20sharpening%2C%20one%20for%20fine%20sharpening%2C%20and%20one%20for%20polishing)%20were%20the%20best%20knife%20sharpeners%2C%20while%20a%20fourth%2C%20for%20scissors%20and%20serrated%20blades%2C%20offered%20the%20most%20versatility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHow%20we%20tested%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Several%20chef's%20knives%20laid%20on%20top%20of%20a%20cutting%20board%20beside%20a%20bowl%20of%20tomatoes.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60302682bed5c50011a2bab7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20ran%20knives%20through%2011%20sharpeners%2C%20weeding%20out%20ones%20that%20clearly%2C%20off%20the%20bat%2C%20weren't%20working%20as%20well%20as%20others.%3Cp%3EOwen%20Burke%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20dulled%20different%20types%20of%20knives%20for%20this%20guide%2C%20ranging%20from%20lower-quality%20440%20stainless%20steel%20(including%20a%20cheap%20pocket%20knife)%20to%20mid-quality%20X50CrMoV15%20steel%20to%20finer%20VG-10%20(relatively%20high-carbon%20steel%20with%20vanadium%20and%20chromium%20and%20molybdenum%20for%20a%20hybrid%20between%20German-%20and%20Japanese-style%20blades).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20ran%20sharpened%20knives%20through%20a%20sheet%20of%20paper%20and%20along%20the%20outward%20sheet%20of%20a%20folded%20high-gloss%20magazine%2C%20which%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DxRPrswhMdAc%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBob%20Kramer's%20method%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20testing%20sharpness.%20We%20then%20took%20them%20back%20to%20the%20kitchen%20to%20see%20if%20they%20could%20slice%20tomatoes%20and%20skin-on%20onions%20under%20little%20to%20no%20more%20than%20their%20own%20weight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConvenience%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Above%20all%2C%20a%20sharpener%20must%20be%20simple%20enough%20to%20use%20that%20it%20doesn't%20prevent%20you%20from%20ever%20actually%20using%20it.%20We%20made%20sure%20that%20each%20sharpener%20we%20tested%20worked%20with%20basic%20instructions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESpeed%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20also%20took%20note%20of%20efficiency%3A%20how%20long%20did%20it%20take%20to%20sharpen%20a%20knife%20sufficiently%3F%20Although%2C%20convenience%20and%20quality%20are%20generally%20non-correlative.%20Specifically%2C%20when%20pull-through%20sharpeners%20were%20quick%20to%20sharpen%2C%20they%20usually%20left%20edges%20fairly%20rough%20and%20jagged.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESafety%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Sharpening%20knives%20can%20be%20dangerous%2C%20so%20a%20stable%20device%20is%20paramount%20to%20ensuring%20safety.%20Some%20options%20we%20tried%20didn't%20necessarily%20inspire%20confidence%20in%20that%20department%2C%20so%20they%20were%20set%20aside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaterials%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20found%20that%20kits%20with%20whetstones%20offered%20the%20most%20precision%2C%20but%20a%20combination%20of%20diamond%20and%20ceramic%20pull-through%20options%20offered%20a%20lot%20for%20the%20relatively%20quick%20pass%20most%20home%20cooks%20are%20willing%20to%20give%20their%20knives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESize%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Some%20sharpeners%20fit%20in%20drawers%2C%20some%20require%20a%20devoted%20shelf%20within%20a%20cabinet%2C%20and%20others%20fit%20in%20your%20pocket.%20Larger%20sharpeners%20performed%20better%20almost%20across%20the%20board%2C%20but%20we%20also%20considered%20the%20needs%20of%20those%20looking%20for%20a%20portable%20sharpener.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20spoke%20with%20metallurgist%20and%20MIT%20senior%20lecturer%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdmse.mit.edu%2Ffaculty%2Fmichael-j-tarkanian%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMichael%20J.%20Tarkanian%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Pat%20LaFrieda%2C%20the%20famed%20butcher%20behind%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flafrieda.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%2