%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPressure%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Whether%20washing%20dishes%20or%20using%20a%20hose%2C%20anyone%20who%20has%20used%20water%20to%20clean%20knows%20that%20stronger%20pressure%20means%20an%20easier%2C%20more%20thorough%20cleaning.%20Well%2C%20the%20same%20is%20true%20using%20a%20bidet.%20Since%20I%20don't%20have%20a%20device%20for%20measuring%20PSI%2C%20this%20was%20a%20subjective%20test%20based%20on%20my%20experiences.%20I%20tend%20to%20like%20very%20strong%20pressure.%20It%20received%20high%20marks%20if%20a%20unit%20was%20strong%20enough%20for%20me%20and%20featured%20at%20least%20three%20pressure%20adjustment%20options%2C%20including%20a%20gentle%20flow%20for%20sensitive%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWater%20temperature%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Upping%20the%20temperature%20of%20the%20water%20you're%20cleaning%20with%20will%20also%20help.%20So%2C%20I%20looked%20for%20bidet%20toilet%20seats%20that%20can%20produce%20hot%20water%2C%20usually%20around%20100%20degrees%20Fahrenheit%2C%20which%20is%20not%20so%20hot%20that%20it%20will%20scald%20you%20but%20warm%20enough%20to%20get%20the%20job%20done.%20I%20tested%20the%20temperature%20by%20running%20the%20bidet%20on%20its%20highest%20water%20temperature%2C%20collecting%20the%20water%20in%20a%20container%2C%20and%20measuring%20it%20with%20a%20probe%20thermometer.%20I%20also%20looked%20for%20at%20least%20three%20temperature%20options%20in%20addition%20to%20ambient.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESeat%20fit%20and%20look%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20If%20the%20seat%20doesn't%20fit%20right%20on%20your%20toilet%2C%20it%20won't%20function%20properly%20and%20will%20look%20awful.%20I%20took%20notes%20on%20how%20easy%20it%20was%20to%20install%20the%20seat%20securely.%20I%20also%20assessed%20how%20good%20the%20seat%20felt%20on%20my%20posterior%20and%20whether%20the%20lid%20was%20supportive%20and%20comfortable%20to%20sit%20on.%20Lastly%2C%20I%20looked%20at%20how%20attractive%20it%20looks%20on%20the%20toilet.%20Were%20the%20cords%20and%20hoses%20sticking%20out%20everywhere%3F%20Did%20the%20controls%20look%20ugly%20or%20intimidating%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENozzle%20positions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20We're%20all%20made%20differently%20and%20have%20different%20preferences.%20Bidets%20should%20have%20enough%20nozzle%20positions%20to%20deliver%20water%20right%20where%20you%20want%20it%20without%20making%20you%20move%20around%20a%20lot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EExtra%20features%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20The%20best%20bidets%20have%20several%20less-than-necessary%20features%20that%20just%20make%20bathroom%20trips%20more%20enjoyable.%20At%20the%20top%20of%20the%20list%20is%20drying.%20Next%20is%20a%20heated%20seat%2C%20especially%20on%20those%20cold%20winter%20mornings.%20And%2C%20if%20you%20have%20a%20youngster%20in%20the%20house%2C%20you'll%20want%20a%20bidet%20that%20only%20activates%20when%20significant%20pressure%20is%20applied%20to%20the%20seat%2C%20like%20when%20you're%20sitting%20on%20it.%20Otherwise%2C%20your%20young%20one%20can%20send%20water%20everywhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWarranty%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20All%20but%20four%20of%20the%20bidets%20we%20tested%20have%20one-year%20warranties.%20The%20four%20outliers%20have%20three-year%20warranties%2C%20each%20costing%20more%20than%20%24500.%20In%20my%205%2B%20years%20of%20owning%20bidets%2C%20I've%20never%20experienced%20a%20malfunction%2C%20but%20if%20you%20are%20particularly%20risk-averse%2C%20you%20may%20want%20to%20choose%20a%20bidet%20with%20a%20longer%20warranty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3EBidet%20FAQs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20do%20you%20install%20a%20bidet%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fhow-to-install-a-bidet-toilet-seat%5C%22%3Einstall%20a%20bidet%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20remove%20your%20toilet%20set.%20Then%2C%20turn%20off%20your%20toilet's%20water%20supply.%20In