0meet%20me%20in%20various%20places%20around%20the%20world.%20We%20pre-booked%20flights%20and%20hotels%20in%20certain%20destinations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Adam%20in%20front%20of%20a%20Miray%20sign%20in%20Istanbul.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ca6f366e2e190e71a39fe3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAdam%20in%20front%20of%20a%20Miray%20sign%20in%20Istanbul.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Adam%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20by%20August%2C%20things%20started%20to%20get%20rather%20strange.%20Miray%20kept%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flife-at-sea-never-ending-cruise-does-not-have-ship-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echanging%20their%20story%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20changing%20their%20agreements.%20They%20kept%20trying%20to%20change%20the%20contract%20I%20had%20signed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20asked%20about%20a%20contract%20withdrawal.%20But%20we%20were%20very%20quickly%20told%20that%20while%20we%20could%20cancel%20and%20withdraw%2C%20our%20refund%20would%20be%20far%20reduced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20they%20tried%20to%20keep%20us%20tied%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%5BEthem%20Bayramo%C4%9Flu%2C%20COO%20of%20Miray%20Cruises%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20Miray%20never%20told%20its%20would-be%20travelers%20this%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20company%20will%20pay%20everyone%20%26quot%3Beven%20if%20they%20have%20withdrawn%20their%20contracts.%20Some%20of%20them%20still%20continue%20with%20their%20contract%20for%20a%202024%20sailing%2C%20and%20we%20will%20pay%20in%20full%20to%20the%20ones%20who%20want%20a%20refund.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHowever%2C%20would-be%20travelers%20like%20Adam%20said%20they%20have%20not%20received%20their%20refunded%20payment.%5D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20September%2C%20management%20at%20Miray%20went%20totally%20silent.%20No%20comm