%20between%20the%20government%20and%20the%20farmer%20groups%20to%20withdraw%20the%20cases%20filed%20against%20them%20during%20the%20year-long%20protest%20against%20the%20now-scrapped%20controversial%20farm%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20meeting%20ended%20before%20both%20sides%20could%20work%20out%20a%20solution%20to%20the%20demand%20for%20minimum%20support%20price%20(MSP)%20guarantee%20law%2C%20farm%20loan%20waiver%2C%20and%20implementation%20of%20the%20Swaminathan%20Commission's%20recommendations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20massive%20deployment%20of%20police%20and%20paramilitary%20personnel%2C%20besides%20multi-layered%20barricading%20have%20been%20made%20to%20seal%20the%20city%20at%20Singhu%2C%20Tikri%2C%20and%20Ghazipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Samyukta%20Kisan%20Morcha%20(Non-Political)%20and%20the%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Morcha%20have%20announced%20that%20more%20than%20200%20farmer%20unions%20would%20head%20to%20Delhi%20to%20press%20the%20Centre%20to%20accept%20their%20demands%2C%20including%20the%20enactment%20of%20a%20law%20to%20guarantee%20a%20minimum%20support%20price%20(MSP)%20for%20crops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20ministers%2C%20including%20Food%20and%20Consumer%20Affairs%20Minister%20Piyush%20Goyal%20and%20Agriculture%20Minister%20Arjun%20Munda%2C%20held%20the%20second%20round%20of%20talks%20with%20the%20farmer%20leaders%20at%20the%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20State%20Institute%20of%20Public%20Administration%20in%20Chandigarh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20press%20conference%2C%20Arjun%20Munda%20said%20that%20issues%20can%20be%20resolved%20through%20dialogue.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20still%20hopeful%20and%20we%20welcome%20talks%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESKM%20(Non-Political)%20leader%20Jagjit%20Singh%20Dallewal%20and%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Sangharsh%20Committee%20general%20secretary%20Sarwan%20Singh%20Pandher%2C%20among%20others%2C%20attended%20the%20meeting%20that%20went%20on%20for%20over%20four%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20meeting%20with%20the%20Union%20ministers%20was%20held%20on%20February%208%2C%20in%20which%20detailed%20discussions%20with%20the%20leaders%20of%20farmer%20organisations%20took%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20tractor-trolleys%20in%20large%20numbers%20set%20out%20from%20different%20parts%20of%20Punjab%20to%20join%20the%20planned%20farmers'%20march%20towards%20Delhi.%20The%20farmer%20leaders%20who%20later%20participated%20in%20the%20talks%20in%20Chandigarh%20held%20a%20meeting%20in%20Amb%20Sahib%20in%20Punjab's%20Mohali%20before%20leaving%20for%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20authorities%20in%20Haryana%20have%20fortified%20the%20state's%20borders%20with%20Punjab%20at%20many%20places%20in%20Ambala%2C%20Jind%2C%20Fatehabad%2C%20Kurukshetra%2C%20and%20Sirsa%20using%20concrete%20blocks%2C%20iron%20nails%2C%20and%20barbed%20wire%20to%20scuttle%20the%20proposed%20march.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Haryana%20government%20has%20imposed%20restrictions%20on%20gathering%20of%20large%20groups%20of%20people%20in%2015%20districts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20a%20legal%20guarantee%20for%20MSP%2C%20the%20farmers%20are%20also%20demanding%20implementation%20of%20the%20Swaminathan%20Commission's%20recommendations%2C%20pensions%20for%20farmers%20and%20farm%20labourers%2C%20farm%20debt%20waiver%2C%20withdrawal%20of%20police%20cases%20and%20%26quot%3Bjustice%26quot%3B%20for%20victims%20of%20the%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%20violence%2C%20reinstatement%20of%20the%20Land%20Acquisition%20Act%2C%202013%2C%20withdrawal%20from%20the%20World%20Trade%20Organisation%2C%20and%20compensation%20for%20families%20of%20farmers%20who%20died%20during%20the%20previous%202020%20agitation%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETraffic%20restrictions%20have%20been%20put%20in%20place%20and%20security%20arrangements%20intensified%20at%20the%20Singhu%2C%20Ghazipur%20and%20Tikri%20borders%20in%20Delhi.%20The%20police%20are%20using%20drones%20to%20keep%20an%20eye%20on%20the%20ground%20situation%2C%20and%20are%20fully%20prepared%20to%20deal%20with%20any%20law%20and%20order%20situation%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMotorists%20had%20a%20hard%20time%20commuting%20between%20Delhi%20and%20town%20in%20the%20National%20Capital%20Region%20(NCR)%20on%20Monday.%20The%20Haryana%20Police%20and%20the%20Chandigarh%20Police%20have%20already%20issued%20traffic%20advisories%2C%20asking%20commuters%20to%20take%20alternative%20routes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20meeting%20with%20Union%20ministers%2C%20farmers'%20leader%20Dallewal%20alleged%20many%20agriculturists%2C%20who%20were%20coming%20from%20other%20states%2C%20including%20Karnataka%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20to%20support%20the%20'Delhi%20Chalo'%20march%2C%20have%20been%20detained%2C%20and%20sought%20their%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDallewal%20claimed%20that%20several%20farmers%20coming%20from%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Karnataka%2C%20owing%20allegiance%20to%20the%20SKM%2C%20have%20been%20detained%20in%20Bhopal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20one%20side%2C%20they%20(the%20Centre)%20are%20holding%20dialogues%20with%20us%20and%20on%20the%20other%20hand%20they%20are%20detaining%20our%20people.%20Then%20how%20will%20this%20dialogue%20take%20place%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20SKM%20(Non-Political)%20leader%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707766260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F0bhqv0n8_farmers_625x300_12_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F5-hour-long-centre-and-farmers-meet-ends-cops-prep-to-face-delhi-chalo-5045843%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Farmers%20leaders%20who%20met%20Union%20ministers%20in%20Chandigarh%20for%20over%20six%20hours%20alleged%20the%20government%20was%20not%20sincere%20about%20the%20talks%2C%20even%20as%20tractor-trolleys%20set%20out%20from%20different%20parts%20of%20Punjab%20to%20go%20to%20Delhi.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUr