%20would%20be%20Ms%20Gandhi%20Vadra's%20first%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESonia%20Gandhi%2C%2077%2C%20who%20has%20not%20been%20keeping%20well%2C%20is%20likely%20to%20file%20nomination%20from%20Jaipur%20in%20the%20coming%20round%20of%20Rajya%20Sabha%20election%2C%20sources%20said.%20They%2C%20however%2C%20added%20that%20Mrs%20Gandhi%20is%20not%20keen%20to%20shift%20to%20Rajya%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20Congress%2C%20it%20would%20be%20a%20huge%20Change%20of%20Guard.%20Mrs%20Gandhi%20has%20been%20representing%20Raebareli%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20since%202006.%20She%20had%20won%20the%20seat%20even%20in%202019%2C%20when%20the%20Congress%20performance%20was%20at%20its%20all-time%20low%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20lost%20the%20other%20family%20turf%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20--%20Amethi%20--%20to%20the%20BJP's%20Smriti%20Irani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%2C%20whose%20entry%20in%20electoral%20politics%20has%20been%20speculated%20on%20for%20decades%2C%20this%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20safe%20seat.%C2%A0%20The%20constituency%2C%20a%20Congress%20bastion%20since%201950s%2C%20was%20first%20represented%20by%20her%20grandfather%20Feroze%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20expected%20that%20Ms%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20would%20contest%20in%202019%20when%20she%20formally%20entered%20politics%20in%20January%20that%20year.%20Many%20had%20hoped%20for%20a%20face-off%20between%20her%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%20Varanasi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20was%20heading%20the%20party%20that%20time%2C%20entrusted%20her%20with%20rejuvenating%20the%20party%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20as%20the%20AICC%20General%20Secretary%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20eastern%20part%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20then%20as%20the%20General%20Secretary%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20entire%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20effort%20had%20crash-landed%20with%20the%20BJP's%20massive%20victory%20from%20the%20state%20in%202019%20and%20Yo