ia%2C%20shared%20a%20world%20map%2C%20highlighting%20the%20countries%20where%C2%A0Indians%20can%20use%20UPI%20to%20make%20payments.%20France%2C%20UAE%2C%20Mauritius%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20Singapore%2C%20Bhutan%2C%20and%20Nepal%20are%20the%20countries%20that%20accept%20UPI%20payments%2C%20according%20to%20the%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''UPI%20goes%20Global!%20India's%20Unified%20Payments%20Interface%20goes%20International%20with%20launches%20in%20Sri%20Lanka%20and%20Mauritius!%20%C2%A0An%20instant%2C%20one-stop%20payment%20interface%20showcases%20'Make%20in%20India%2C%20Make%20for%20the%20World%2C''%20the%20tweet%20read.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere's%20the%20tweet%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EUPI%20goes%20Global!%F0%9F%A4%A9%3Cbr%3E%5CnIndia's%20Unified%20Payments%20Interface%20goes%20International%20with%20launches%20in%20Sri%20Lanka%20and%20Mauritius!%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAn%20instant%2C%20one-stop%20payment%20interface%20showcases%20'Make%20in%20India%2C%20Make%20for%20the%20World'.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FDigitalPayment%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23DigitalPayment%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FRuPay%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23RuPay%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FEI8LBWxZCi%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FEI8LBWxZCi%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20MyGovIndia%20(%40mygovindia)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmygovindia%2Fstatus%2F1757033844832604330%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2012%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20been%20proactive%20in%20extending%20the%20reach%20of%20UPI%20globally.%20Last%20year%2C%20India%20also%20showcased%20the%20UPI%20system%20at%20the%20G20%20meetings%2C%20enabling%20the%20delegates%20to%20experience%20real-time%20transactions%20over%20the%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20UPI%20services%20were%20rolled%20out%20in%20Sri%20Lanka%20and%20Mauritius%2C%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20describing%20it%20as%20linking%20historic%20ties%20with%20modern%20digital%20technology.%20In%20his%20remarks%2C%20PM%20Modi%20hoped%20the%20new%20fintech%20services%20would%20help%20the%20two%20nations%20and%20said%20the%20UPI%20is%20implementing%20%26quot%3Bnew%20responsibilities%20of%20uniting%20partners%20with%20India%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20that%2C%C2%A0the%20payment%20system%20was%20formally%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fupi-services-launched-in-france-at-eiffel-tower-after-macrons-india-visit-4981830%5C%22%3E%20launched%20at%20the%20Eiffel%20Tower%20in%20Paris%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20on%20February%202.%C2%A0Notably%2C%20Bhutan%20was%20the%20first%20country%20to%20enable%20UPI%20transactions%20through%20the%20BHIM%20app.%20The%20UPI%20digital%20payment%20app%20was%20virtually%20launched%20on%20July%2013%2C%202021%2C%20by%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20and%20her%20Bhutanese%20counterpart%20Lyonpo%20Namgay%20Tshering.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjapan-may-soon-accept-indias-upi-payment-system-report-4050240%5C%22%3Ereport%20suggested%20that%20Japan%3C%2Fa%3E%20might%20also%C2%A0join%20India's%20UPI%20payment%20system%20and%20promote%20cooperation%20on%20the%20digital%20identity%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeveloped%20by%20the%20National%20Payments%20Corporation%20of%20India%20(NPCI)%2C%20UPI%20is%20an%20instant%20real-time%20payment%20system%20to%20facilitate%20inter-bank%20transactions%20through%20mobile%20phones.%20It%20powers%20multiple%20bank%20accounts%20into%20a%20single%20mobile%20application%20(of%20any%20participating%20bank)%2C%20merging%20several%20banking%20features%2C%20seamless%20fund%20routing%2C%20and%20merchant%20payments%20into%20one%20hood.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707756900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fttv8pm0o_upi-payments_625x300_12_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgovernment-releases-list-of-countries-where-upi-payments-are-accepted-5045322%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22UPI%20is%20an%20instant%20real-time%20payment%20system%20to%20facilitate%20inter-bank%20transactions%20through%20mobile%20phones.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgovernment-releases-list-of-countries-where-upi-payments-are-accepted-5045322%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgovernment-releases-list-of-countries-where-upi-payments-are-accepted-5045322%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgovernment-releases-list-of-countries-where-upi-payments-are-accepted-5045322%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pakistan%20Elections%3A%20In%20the%20Face%20of%20a%20Hegemonic%20Establishment%2C%20People%20Have%20Shown%20the%20Way%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F06200923%2FEffect-2024-02-06T200834.583.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EImran%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20victory%20despite%20the%20odds%20stacked%20against%20him%20has%20stunned%20the%20world.%20In%20many%20constituencies%2C%20independent%20candidates%20fielded%20by%20his%20Pakistan%20Tehreek-e-Insaf%20(PTI)%20trounced%20political%20heavyweights%2C%20unseating%20them%20from%20their%20traditional%20bastions.%20This%20was%20no%20easy%20feat%20to%20achieve%2C%20given%20that%20the%20establishment%20%E2%80%93%20undoubtedly%20the%20most%20powerful%20institution%20controlling%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20affairs%20%E2%80%93%20went%20all%20out%20to%20intimidate%20and%20harass%20the%20