0prevail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F07171745%2FEffect-2024-02-07T171716.436.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F07171745%2FEffect-2024-02-07T171716.436.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F07171745%2FEffect-2024-02-07T171716.436-300x140.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F07171745%2FEffect-2024-02-07T171716.436-1024x478.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-696087%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ELeft%20to%20Right%3A%20Nawaz%20Sharif%2C%20Bilawal%20Bhutto%20Zardari%2C%20and%20Imran%20Khan.%20The%20three%20are%20in%20the%20race%20for%20prime%20ministership.%20Photos%3A%20Pakistan%20flag%20in%20the%20background%20(Wikimedia%20Commons%2FPublic%20Domain)%3B%20Nawaz%20Sharif%20(Wikimedia%20Commons%2FZ%20A%20Balti%2FPublic%20Domain)%20Bilawal%20Bhutto%20Zardari%20(Wikimedia%20Commons%2FU.S.%20Department%20of%20State%2F%20Public%20Domain)%3B%20and%20Imran%20Khan%20(Wikimedia%20Commons%2FThe%20White%20House%2FPublic%20Domain).%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20results%20started%20trickling%20out%2C%20I%20was%20miles%20away%20from%20Kashmir%20in%20Medina%20for%20Umrah.%20It%20was%20a%20chance%20encounter%20with%20a%20young%20Pakistani%20Pashtun%20that%20got%20me%20thinking.%20Even%20though%20I%20rightly%20guessed%20his%20nationality%2C%20he%20appeared%20reluctant%20to%20admit%20it.%20His%20forehead%20was%20furrowed%20with%20lines%20that%20gave%20away%20his%20disgust%20and%20disenchantment.%20As%20I%20asked%20him%20about%20the%20situation%20unravelling%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20he%20chose%20not%20to%20mince%20his%20words%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Ehalat%20toh%20kharab%20hi%20hain.%20Humare%20Pathan%20kay%20sath%20dekho%20kya%20kiya%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9C.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20young%20man%20was%20completely%20disillusioned%20with%20what%20was%20happening%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20and%20the%20treatment%20meted%20out%20to%20his%20leader%20only%20exacerbated%20the%20sense%20of%20brewing%20bitterness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistan-election-pml-n-hold-talks-with-ppp-us-uk-eu-express-concerns-over-process%5C%22%3EPakistan%20Election%3A%20PML-N%20Hold%20Talks%20with%20PPP%3B%20US%2C%20UK%2C%20EU%20Raise%20Concerns%20Over%20Irregularities%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20sense%20of%20%3Cem%3Edeja%20vu%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20time%20an%20election%20exposed%20ethnic%20fault%20lines%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20this%20led%20to%20its%20eventual%20dismemberment%20with%20the%20creation%20of%20Bangladesh%2C%20formerly%20known%20as%20East%20Pakistan.%20Sheikh%20Mujibur%20Rehman%2C%20a%20revolutionary%20leader%20adored%20by%20Pakistani%20Bengalis%2C%20was%20also%20stripped%20of%20his%20rightful%20victory%20by%20the%20then%20establishment%2C%20followed%20by%20a%20violent%20crackdown%20on%20its%20people.%20The%20mass%20denial%20of%20democratic%20rights%20and%20civil%20liberties%20to%20the%20Bengalis%20stirred%20a%20revolt%20%E2%80%93%20the%20outcome%20of%20which%20was%20another%20partition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%E2%80%99s%20grim%20situation%20not%20only%20shares%20a%20worrying%20parallel%20with%20the%20period%20that%20led%20to%20East%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20secession.%20It%20also%20coincides%20with%20a%20severe%20economic%20crisis%20and%20a%20sudden%20surge%20in%20terror%20incidents.%20There%20is%20simmering%20resentment%20in%20Balochistan%20%26amp%3B%20Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa%20against%20the%20establishment%20for%20stealing%20and%20exploiting%20their%20natural%20resources%20while%20they%20live%20in%20abject%20poverty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20repeating%20the%20wrongs%20of%20history%2C%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20all-powerful%20state%20could%20yet%20again%20plunge%20the%20country%20into%20further%20chaos%20and%20political%20instability.%20Denying%20the%20youth%20who%20en%20masse%20voted%20for%20Imran%20Khan%20will%20have%20a%20cascading%20effect%20of%20street%20protests%20alternating%20with%20a%20vicious%20cycle%20of%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scenes%20playing%20out%20in%20Pakistan%20have%20evoked%20a%20sense%20of%20%3Cem%3Edeja%20vu%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%2C%20who%20have%20experienced%20their%20fair%20share%20of%20subjugation%20of%20democratic%20rights.%20The%20genesis%20of%20the%20growing%20sense%20of%20alienation%20can%20be%20traced%20back%20to%20the%20shambolic%201951%20elections%20to%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%2C%20which%20was%20to%20ratify%20the%20former%20princely%20state%E2%80%99s%20accession%20to%20the%20Union%20of%20India.%20The%20voice%20of%20dissent%20was%20crushed%20in%20one%20fell%20swoop%2C%20which%20shook%20the%20faith%20of%20Kashmiris%20in%20the%20newly%20found%20democratic%20process.%20This%20became%20a%20recurring%20pattern%20and%20template%20to%20manipulate%20and%20erode%20the%20popular%20will%20for%20years%20to%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20were%20exceptions%20like%201977%2C%20the%20turning%20point%20came%20with%20the%20brazenly%20rigged%20election%20in%201987%20which%20acted%20as%20a%20catalyst%20for%20the%20insurgency%20that%20engulfed%20the%20state%20in%20a%20vortex%20of%20violence.%20To%20this%20day%2C%20the%20people%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20continue%20to%20suffer%20and%20pay%20a%20price%20with%20their%20lives%20upended%20by%20the%20continuing%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%E2%80%99s%20powerful%20establishment%20may%20have%20denied%20Imran%20Khan%20his%20rightful%20victory%20but%20by%20doing%20so%20they%20are%20also%20depriving%20millions%20of%20Pakistans%20their%20agency%20and%20their%20right%20to%20choose%2C%20especially%20at%20a%20time%20when%20they%20are%20already%20reeling%20under%20a%20severe%20economic%20and%20political%20crisis.%20In%20these%20circumstances%2C%20undermining%20the%20popular%20mandate%20will%20only%20serve%20as%20a%20pyrrhic%20victory.%20Assuming%20that%20a%20non-PTI%20government%20through%20permutations%20will%20be%20thrust%20on%20the%20people%2C%20one%20can%20only%20imagine%20the%20further%20instability%20this%20could%20bring%20to%20a%20country%20already%20on%20the%20brink%20of%20chaos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMehbooba%20Mufti%20is%20president%20of%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Peoples%20Democratic%20Party%20and%20a%20former%20chief%20minister%20of%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707756508000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F06200923%2FEffect-2024-02-06T200834.583.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistan-elections-in-the-face-of-a-hegemonic-establishment-people-have-shown-the-way%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Today%E2%80%99s%20situation%20shares%20a%20worrying%20parallel%20with%20the%20period%20that%20led%20to%20East%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20secession%2C%20given%20the%20resentment%20in%20Balochistan%20and%20Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa%20against%20the%20establishment%20for%20exploiting%20their%20resources.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistan-elections-in-the-face-of-a-hegemonic-establishment-people-have-shown-the-way%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BPay%20MNREGA%20Dues%26quot%3B%3A%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20Letter%20To%20PM%20An%20Overture%20To%20Trinamool%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECongress's%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20added%20voice%20to%20Bengal%20Chief