%20speech%20from%20Mr%20Chaudhary%20on%20the%20subject%20that%20had%20kept%20the%20Opposition%2C%20especially%20Akhilesh%20Yadav's%20Samajwadi%20party%20on%20tenterhooks%20so%20far.%20On%20Friday%2C%20asked%20whether%20he%20was%20ready%20to%20join%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%2045-year-old%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIs%20there%20anything%20left%20to%20be%20done%3F%20How%20can%20I%20refuse%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20BJP%20had%20made%20its%20offer%20to%20the%20RLD%20that%20week%2C%20promising%20a%20Rajya%20Sabha%20seat%2C%20two%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20(Baghpat%20and%20Bijnor%20likely)%20and%20two%20ministerial%20berths%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Mr%20Chaudhary%20had%20been%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20acceptance.%20Then%20the%20BJP%20sweetened%20the%20deal%20on%20Friday%20with%20a%20Bharat%20Ratna%20for%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%2C%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20the%20grandfather%20of%20Mr%20Chaudhary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDil%20jeet%20liya%20mera%20(They%20have%20won%20my%20heart)%2C%26quot%3B%20Jayant%20Chaudhary%20had%20said%20on%20the%20occasion%2C%20after%20which%20he%20was%20asked%20whether%20he%20was%20ready%20to%20join%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20defection%20of%20the%20RLD%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20Nitish%20Kumar%20in%20Bihar%20will%20reinforce%20the%20perception%20that%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20is%20a%20united%20front%20and%20give%20credence%20to%20the%20BJP's%20divided%20house%20claims.%20Besides%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnArvind%20Kejriwal%20with%20his%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20and%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20with%20her%20Trinamool%20Congress%20have%20already%20done%20the%20heavy%20lifting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20change%20of%20camp%20by%20the%20RLD%20is%20also%20likely%20to%20cost%20the%20bloc%20a%20chunk%20of%20Jat%20votes%20in%20western%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20While%20the%20party%20may%20not%20have%20the%20heft%20to%20win%20too%20many%20seats%20on%20its%20own%2C%20the%20support%20of%20Jats%20can%20make%20the%20difference%