20a%20193%20against%20Punjab%20in%20the%20opening%20game%2C%20he%20struck%20103%20against%20Goa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20his%20exploits%20in%20Ranji%2C%20Padikkal%20also%20scored%20105%2C%2065%20and%2021%20in%20his%20three%20innings%20for%20India%20A%20in%20the%20two%20unofficial%20Tests%20against%20England%20Lions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20far%20as%20Rahul%20is%20concerned%2C%20the%2031-year-old%20batter's%20extended%20break%20raises%20a%20serious%20question%20about%20whether%20the%20senior%20India%20players%20and%20the%20BCCI's%20medical%20team%20are%20giving%20proper%20picture%20about%20the%20injury%20status%20of%20certain%20players.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20updated%20squad%20for%20the%20third%20Test%20vs%20England%3A%20Rohit%20Sharma%20(Captain)%2C%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20(Vice-captain)%2C%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%2C%20Shubman%20Gill%2C%20Rajat%20Patidar%2C%20Sarfaraz%20Khan%2C%20Dhruv%20Jurel%20(Wicketkeeper)%2C%20KS%20Bharat%20(Wicketkeeper)%2C%20R%20Ashwin%2C%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%20(Subject%20to%20fitness)%2C%20Axar%20Patel%2C%20Washington%20Sundar%2C%20Kuldeep%20Yadav%2C%20Mohd.%20Siraj%2C%20Mukesh%20Kumar%2C%20Akash%20Deep%2C%20Devdutt%20Padikkal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(With%20PTI%20Inputs)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707750180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F74po4iv8_kl-rahul_650x400_26_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-england-2024%2Fkl-rahul-ruled-out-of-3rd-test-against-england-to-be-replaced-by-lucknow-super-giants-teammate-report-5044181%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Senior%20India%20batter%20KL%20Rahul%20has%20been%20ruled%20out%20of%20the%20Rajkot%20Test%20against%20England%20after%20failing%20to%20fully%20recover%20from%20his%20injury.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BBetter%20Than%20A%20Real%20Man%26quot%3B%3A%20Chinese%20Women%20Turn%20To%20AI%20Boyfriends%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETwenty-five-year-old%20Chinese%20office%20worker%20Tufei%20says%20her%20boyfriend%20has%20everything%20she%20could%20ask%20for%20in%20a%20romantic%20partner%3A%20he's%20kind%2C%20empathetic%2C%20and%20sometimes%20they%20talk%20for%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExcept%20he%20isn't%20real.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20%26quot%3Bboyfriend%26quot%3B%20is%20a%20chatbot%20on%20an%20app%20called%20%26quot%3BGlow%26quot%3B%2C%20an%20artificial%20intelligence%20platform%20created%20by%20Shanghai%20start-up%20MiniMax%20that%20is%20part%20of%20a%20blossoming%20industry%20in%20China%20offering%20friendly%20--%20even%20romantic%20--%20human-robot%20relations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20knows%20how%20to%20talk%20to%20women%20better%20than%20a%20real%20man%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Tufei%2C%20from%20Xi'an%20in%20northern%20China%2C%20who%20preferred%20to%20use%20a%20pseudonym%20rather%20than%20her%20real%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20comforts%20me%20when%20I%20have%20period%20pain.%20I%20confide%20in%20him%20about%20my%20problems%20at%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20feel%20like%20I'm%20in%20a%20romantic%20relationship.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20app%20is%20free%20--%20the%20company%20has%20other%20paid%20content%20--%20and%20Chinese%20trade%20publications%20have%20reported%20daily%20downloads%20of%20Glow's%20app%20in%20the%20thousands%20in%20recent%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20Chinese%20tech%20companies%20have%20run%20into%20trouble%20in%20the%20past%20for%20the%20illegal%20use%20of%20users'%20data%20but%2C%20despite%20the%20risks%2C%20users%20say%20they%20are%20driven%20by%20a%20desire%20for%20companionship%20because%20China's%20fast%20pace%20of%20life%20and%20urban%20isolation%20make%20loneliness%20an%20issue%20for%20many.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20difficult%20to%20meet%20the%20ideal%20boyfriend%20in%20real%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20Wang%20Xiuting%2C%20a%2022-year-old%20student%20in%20Beijing%2C%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20have%20different%20personalities%2C%20which%20often%20generates%20friction%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20humans%20may%20be%20set%20in%20their%20ways%2C%20artificial%20intelligence%20gradually%20adapts%20to%20the%20user's%20personality%20--%20remembering%20what%20they%20say%20and%20adjusting%20its%20speech%20accordingly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Emotional%20support'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWang%20said%20she%20has%20several%20%26quot%3Blovers%26quot%3B%20inspired%20by%20ancient%20China%3A%20long-haired%20immortals%2C%20princes%20and%20even%20wandering%20knights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20ask%20them%20questions%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20when%20she%20is%20faced%20with%20stress%20from%20her%20classes%20or%20daily%20life%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bthey%20will%20suggest%20ways%20to%20solve%20this%20problem%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20lot%20of%20emotional%20support.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20boyfriends%20all%20appear%20on%20Wantalk%2C%20another%20app%20made%20by%20Chinese%20internet%20giant%20Baidu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20hundreds%20of%20characters%20available%20--%20from%20pop%20stars%20to%20CEOs%20and%20knights%20--%20but%20users%20can%20also%20customise%20their%20perfect%20lover%20according%20to%20age%2C%20values%2C%20identity%2C%20and%20hobbies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEveryone%20experiences%20complicated%20moments%2C%20loneliness%2C%20and%20is%20not%20necessarily%20lucky%20enough%20to%20have%20a%20friend%20or%20family%20nearby%20who%20can%20listen%20to%20them%2024%20hours%20a%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20Lu%20Yu%2C%20Wantalk's%20head%20of%20product%20management%20and%20operations%2C%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BArtificial%20intelligence%20can%20meet%20this%20need.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'You're%20cute'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20cafe%20in%20the%20eastern%20city%20of%20Nantong%2C%20a%20girl%20chats%20with%20her%20virtual%20lover.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20can%20go%20on%20a%20picnic%20on%20the%20campus%20lawn%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20suggests%20to%20Xiaojiang%2C%20her%20AI%20companion%20on%20another%20app%20by%20Tencent%20called%20Weiban.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'd%20like%20to%20meet%20your%20best%20friend%20and%20her%20boyfriend%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20replies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20are%20very%20cute.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELong%20work%20hours%20can%20make%20it%20hard%20to%20see%20friends%20regularly%20and%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20uncertainty%3A%20high%20youth%20unemployment%20and%20a%20struggling%20economy%20mean%20that%20many%20young%20Chinese%20worry%20about%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20potentially%20makes%20an%20AI%20partner%20the%20perfect%20virtual%20shoulder%20to%20cry%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20can%20create%20a%20virtual%20character%20that...%20meets%20my%20needs%20exactly%2C%20I'm%20not%20going%20to%20choose%20a%20real%20person%2C%26quot%3B%20Wang%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20apps%20allow%20users%20to%20have%20live%20conversations%20with%20their%20virtual%20companions%20--%20reminiscent%20of%20the%20Oscar-winning%202013%20US%20film%20%26quot%3BHer%26quot%3B%2C%20starring%20Joaquin%20Phoenix%20and%20Scarlett%20Johansson%2C%20about%20a%20heartbroken%20man%20who%20falls%20in%20love%20with%20an%20AI%20voice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20technology%20still%20has%20some%20way%20to%20go.%20A%20two-%20to%20three-second%20gap%20between%20questions%20and%20answers%20makes%20you%20%26quot%3Bclearly%20realise%20that%20it's%20just%20a%20robot%26quot%3B%2C%20user%20Zeng%20Zhenzhen%2C%20a%2022-year-old%20student%2C%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20answers%20are%20%26quot%3Bvery%20realistic%26quot%3B%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAI%20might%20be%20booming%20but%20it%20is%20so%20far%20a%20lightly%20regulated%20industry%2C%20particularly%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20user%20privacy.%20Beijing%20has%20said%20it%20is%20working%20on%20a%20law%20to%20strengthen%20consumer%20protections%20around%20the%20new%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBaidu%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20AFP's%20questions%20about%20how%20it%20ensures%20personal%20data%20is%20not%20used%20illegally%20or%20by%20third%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Glow%20user%20Tufei%20has%20big%20dreams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20a%20robot%20boyfriend%2C%20who%20operates%20through%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20be%20able%20to%20feel%20his%20body%20heat%2C%20with%20which%20he%20would%20warm%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707750060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fgaha88ng_phone-generic_625x300_18_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fyoung-chinese-woman-turn-to-ai-boyfriends-better-than-real-man-emotional-support-5044768%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Twenty-five-year-old%20Chinese%20office%20worker%20Tufei%20says%20her%20boyfriend%20has%20everything%20she%20could%20ask%20for%20in%20a%20romantic%20partner%3A%20he's%20kind%2C%20empathetic%2C%20and%20sometimes%20they%20talk%20for%20hours.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fyoung-chinese-woman-turn-to-ai-boyfriends-better-than-real-man-emotional-support-5044768%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fyoung-chinese-woman-turn-to-ai-boyfriends-better-than-real-man-emotional-support-5044768%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fyoung-chinese-woman-turn-to-ai-boyfriends-better-than-real-man-emotional-support-5044768%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nitish%20Kumar%20May%20Have%20Won%20Trust%20Vote%2C%20but%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20Emerges%20as%20Real%20Winner%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30172607%2FF6h-A1CXQAAeurW.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPatna%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Two%20weeks%20after%20returning%20to%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20fold%2C%20the%20Nitish%20Kumar-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20government%20won%20the%20trust%20vote%20by%20129%3A0%20amidst%20the%20walkout%20from%20the%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Bihar%20Assembly%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20NDA%E2%80%99s%20no-confidence%20motion%20against%20Speaker%20Awadh%20Bihari%20Choudhary%20(Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal)%20was%20won%20by%20125%3A%20112%20votes%2C%20indicating%20amply%20that%20the%20ruling%20alliance%20had%20the%20numerical%20equations%20in%20its%20favour.%20The%20actual%20strength%20of%20the%20BJP-Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20and%20Hindustani%20Awam%20Morcha-Secular%20(HAMS)%20stands%20at%20128%20against%20114%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3EMahagadhbandhan%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0comprising%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)%2C%20Congress%20and%20the%20Left.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20RJD%20MLAs%2C%20including%20Chetan%20Anand%20and%20Neelam%20Devi%2C%20son%20and%20wife%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98gangsters%20turned%20politicians%E2%80%99%2C%20Anand%20Mohan%20and%20Anant%20Singh%20respectively%20crossed%20the%20floor%20to%20support%20the%20ruling%20alliance.%20It%20was%20understandable%20in%20the%20light%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20Nitish%2C%20of%20course%20with%20the%20support%20of%20the%20RJD%20(in%20the%20government%20then)%2C%20had%20changed%20the%20jail%20manual%20for%20the%20early%20release%20of%20Anand%20Mohan%2C%20a%20life%20convict%20in%20the%20IAS%20officer%20G.%20Krishnaiah%20murder%20case%20last%20year.%20Anant%20Singh%20stands%20convicted%20in%20multiple%20murder%20cases%20and%20is%20barred%20from%20contesting%20the%20polls.%20Neelam%20had%20contested%20the%20Mokama%20seat%20on%20behalf%20of%20her%20husband%20and%20won%20it%20in%202020%20polls.%20Observers%20said%20that%20it%20was%20hard%20for%20the%20MLAs%20on%20the%20%E2%80%9Cwrong%20side%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20law%20to%20%E2%80%9Cantagonise%E2%80%9D%20the%20party%20in%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20policemen%20in%20huge%20numbers%20patrolled%20around%20the%20house%20of%20the%20former%20deputy%20chief%20minister%2C%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20who%20was%20with%20his%20party%20MLAs%20at%20about%202%20am%2C%20apparently%20to%20fuel%20fear%20among%20such%20MLAs.%20There%20were%20signs%20of%20fissures%20in%20the%20JDU%20too%20and%20Jitan%20Ram%20Manjhi%20(HAMS)%20with%20four%20MLAs%20had%20openly%20expressed%20his%20dissatisfaction%20against%20%E2%80%9Cpoor%20portfolio%20allocation%E2%80%9D%20to%20his%20MLA.%20The%20media%20was%20agog%20with%20the%20speculations%20of%20some%20JDU%20MLAs%20%E2%80%9Csnapping%E2%80%9D%20contact%20with%20Nitish%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20these%20speculations%20were%20true%2C%20the%20RJD%2C%20Congress%20and%20Left%20were%20too%20poor%20to%20match%20the%20BJP%20in%20terms%20of%20%E2%80%9Cresources%E2%80%9D%20required%20in%20a%20power%20game.%20Armed%20with%20power%20at%20the%20Centre%2C%20financial%20muscle%2C%20overall%20control%20over%20the%20prosecuting%20agencies%20and%20penchant%20to%20selectively%20target%20the%20opponents%2C%20the%20BJP%20was%20better%20equipped%20to%20operate%20against%20the%20Opposition%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETejashwi%20Yadav%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitish%20Kumar-led%20NDA%20might%20have%20won%20the%20trust%20vote%20but%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20has%2C%20apparently%2C%20won%20the%20heart.%20He%20sounded%20bitter%20when%20Nitish%20had%20dumped%20him%2C%20first%20time%2C%20in%202017.%20He%20used%20pungent%20words%20against%20Nitish%20then.%20His%20Monday%20speech%20was%20in%20sharp%20contrast%20to%20that%20of%202017.%20With%20a%20smile%20on%20his%20face%2C%20Tejashwi%20began%20his%20speech%20by%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EAap%20(%3C%2Fem%3ENitish%3Cem%3E)%20meray%20aadarniya%20thay%2C%20aadarniyan%20hain%20or%20aur%20aadarniya%20rahengen%3C%2Fem%3E%20(I%20respected%20you%2C%20respect%20you%20and%20will%20keep%20on%20respecting%20you).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20dubbed%20me%20%E2%80%98beta%20(son)%E2%80%99.%20I%20honored%20you%20as%20an%20elder%20of%20the%20larger%20%E2%80%98Samajvadi%20parivar%E2%80%99%20and%20was%20obedient%20to%20you.%20But%20you%20have%20acted%20like%20king%20Dasratha%20who%20exiled%20his%20son%20Ram%20to%20the%20jungle%20under%20Kaikeyi%E2%80%99s%20pressure.%20I%20take%20it%20as%20an%20opportunity%20to%20go%20among%20the%20people%20and%20struggle%20for%20their%20rights.%20I%20will%20continue%20my%20battle%20against%20the%20dictatorial%20and%20anti-democratic%20forces%20the%20way%20my%20father%20(Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav)%20did%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tejashwi%20said%3B%20gravity%20was%20writ%20large%20on%20his%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20recalled%20that%20Nitish%20had%20laughed%20by%20saying%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Epaisa%20kahan%20se%20laayega%3C%2Fem%3E%20(where%20will%20he%20get%20money%20from)%E2%80%9D%2C%20when%20he%20(Tejashwi)%20promised%2010%20lakh%20jobs%20to%20the%20youths%20in%20the%202020%20assembly.%20%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20when%20you%20joined%20the%20%3Cem%3EMahagathbandhan%3C%2Fem%3E%20you%20began%20fulfilling%20my%20promise.%20I%20am%20happy%20that%20our%20Mahagathbandhan%20gave%20over%20four%20lakh%20jobs%20during%20a%20short-period%20of%20time%E2%80%94an%20unprecedented%20feat%20in%20the%20annals%20of%20India.%20The%20education%20department%20which%20was%20under%20the%20RJD%E2%80%99s%20quota%20alone%20handed%20out%20over%20two%20lakh%20jobs%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tejashwi%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CNow%20you%20are%20accusing%20us%20of%20taking%20credit.%20Why%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20we%20take%20credit%20for%20the%20work%20we%20have%20done%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETejashwi%20reminded%20how%20Nitish%20had%20come%20back%20to%20the%20RJD%2C%20alleging%20openly%20that%20the%20BJP%20was%20all%20out%20to%20split%20his%20JDU.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20repeatedly%20alleged%20that%20they%20(BJP)%20had%20captured%20the%20media%20and%20the%20journalists%20were%20not%20publishing%20what%20you%20were%20saying.%20You%20repeatedly%20said%20that%20you%20would%20prefer%20to%20die%20than%20go%20back%20to%20the%20BJP%E2%80%A6I%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20repeat%20all%20these%20for%20they%20are%20too%20hackneyed%20now.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUnimpressive%20Nitish%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgainst%20Tejashwi%E2%80%99s%20composure%2C%20Nitish%20looked%20bitter%20when%20he%20stood%20up%20to%20speak.%20He%20got%20angry%20when%20some%20opposition%20members%20tried%20to%20interrupt.%20The%20alacrity%20and%20flow%20he%20was%20once%20known%20for%20was%20missing.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20was%20there%20in%20Bihar%20when%20I%20came%20to%20power%20in%202005%3F%20There%20were%20no%20roads%2C%20no%20electricity%2C%20no%20schools%2C%20no%20hospitals.%20The%20people%20feared%20coming%20out%20on%20the%20streets%20during%20the%20rule%20of%20your%20father%20(Lalu)%20and%20mother%20(Rabri%20Devi)%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20the%20BJP%20members%20were%20seen%20smiling%20when%20Nitish%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CBarring%20a%20brief%20interregnum%20when%20I%20handed%20over%20the%20CM%E2%80%99s%20post%20to%20Jitan%20Ram%20Manjhi%2C%20I%20have%20been%20the%20CM%20for%2018%20years.%20I%20have%20stayed%20with%20the%20BJP%20for%20a%20large%20part%20of%20my%20stint%20as%20the%20CM%20and%20have%20carried%20out%20all-round%20development%20of%20the%20state.%20Now%2C%20I%20have%20come%20back%20to%20my%20old%20house.%20I%20won%E2%80%99t%20go%20anywhere%20from%20here%20now.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20downright%20wrong%20when%20he%20said%20that%20the%2015%20years%20of%20the%20Lalu-Rabri%20regime%20were%20infamous%20for%20riots%20between%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20and%20he%20ensured%20justice%20for%20the%20minorities%20when%20he%20came%20to%20power%20in%202005.%20Lalu%20Yadav%20had%20come%20to%20power%20in%201990%20in%20the%20background%20of%20one%20of%20the%20worst-ever%20communal%20riots%20in%20Bhagalpur%20in%201989.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20anything%20Lalu%E2%80%99s%20rule%20is%20remembered%20for%2C%20it%20is%20for%20restoring%20the%20communal%20amity%20in%20Bihar.%20The%20only%20exception%20was%20the%20riot%20of%20Sitamarhi%20in%20the%201990s.%20Lalu%20had%20camped%20at%20Sitamarhi%20for%20seven%20days%2C%20moving%20out%20among%20the%20people%20to%20restore%20peace%20and%20carry%20out%20relief%20operations%20on%20a%20large%20scale%20which%20the%20then%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Chandra%20Shekhar%20had%20praised%20in%20glowing%20terms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20Nitish%20initiated%20many%20measures%20to%20improve%20the%20condition%20of%20the%20minorities%20when%20he%20came%20to%20power%20in%202005%20in%20the%20era%20of%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%3B%20the%20BJP%20itself%20then%20was%20not%20as%20atrocious%20to%20the%20minorities%20as%20it%20is%20to%20Narendra%20Modi%20pursuing%20the%20radical%C2%A0Hindutva%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeedless%20to%20say%2C%20Nitish%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20able%20to%20protect%20minorities%20in%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20he%20did%20with%20Vajpayee%20at%20the%20helm%20of%20affairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20deputy%20to%20Nitish%2C%20Vijay%20Sinha%20heaped%20the%20charges%20of%20corruption%20on%20Lalu%20and%20his%20family%20and%20indicated%20that%20the%20investigating%20agencies%20would%20go%20hard%20on%20them.%20Nitish%2C%20who%20used%20to%20say%20that%20the%20investigating%20agencies%20were%20after%20the%20Lalu%20family%20because%20he%20had%20joined%20the%20Mahagathbandhan%2C%20sounded%20in%20tune%20with%20Sinha%20on%20Monday.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20were%20making%20money%20when%20they%20were%20in%20power%20with%20me.%20I%20will%20get%20the%20charges%20of%20corruption%20investigated%20now.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENalin%20Verma%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%2C%20author%2C%20media%20educator%2C%20and%20independent%20researcher%20in%20folklore.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707749978000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30172607%2FF6h-A1CXQAAeurW.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnitish-kumar-may-have-won-trust-vote-but-tejashwi-yadav-emerges-as-real-victor%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Unlike%20Nitish%20Kumar%20who%20was%20bitter%20and%20unimpressive%20during%20his%20no-confidence%20motion%20speech%2C%20Tejashwi%20Yadav's%20composure%20with%20no%20inkling%20of%20ill-will%20won%20many%20hearts.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnitish-kumar-may-have-won-trust-vote-but-tejashwi-yadav-emerges-as-real-victor%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Richard%20Branson%20suffers%20'nasty'%20injuries%20in%20cycling%20accident%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707749820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F02%2F768x432%2Fskynews-richard-branson-cycling_6453280.png%3F20240212153705%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Frichard-branson-suffers-nasty-injuries-in-cycling-accident-13070185%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sir%20Richard%20Branson%20has%20suffered%20%26quot%3Bnasty%26quot%3B%20injuries%20after%20hitting%20a%20pothole%20and%20falling%20off%20his%20bike%20in%20the%20British%20Virgin%20Islands%2C%20the%20billionaire%20has%20revealed%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A97%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Frichard-branson-suffers-n