A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fioc-arcelormittal-nippon-steel-to-resolve-dispute-through-arbitration-sc-124021201327_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20dispute%20is%20related%20to%20Essar%20Steel%20India%20Limited%20(ESIL)%2C%20which%20was%20acquired%20by%20AMNS%20through%20the%20insolvency%20resolution%20process%20in%202019.%20This%20was%20approved%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fioc-arcelormittal-nippon-steel-to-resolve-dispute-through-arbitration-sc-124021201327_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fioc-arcelormittal-nippon-steel-to-resolve-dispute-through-arbitration-sc-124021201327_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fioc-arcelormittal-nippon-steel-to-resolve-dispute-through-arbitration-sc-124021201327_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Farooq%20Abdullah%20Summoned%20For%20Questioning%20In%20Money%20Laundering%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EVeteran%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20leader%20and%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Farooq%20Abdullah%20has%20again%20been%20summoned%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20in%20an%20alleged%20money%20laundering%20case.%20The%2086-year-old%2C%20who%20represents%20Srinagar%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20was%20summoned%20in%20the%20same%20case%20last%20month.%20But%20citing%20health%20reasons%2C%20he%20did%20not%20appear%20at%20the%20offices%20of%20the%20agency%20in%20Srinagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20the%20latest%20Opposition%20leader%20--%20after%20Jharkhand's%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Hemant%20Soren%20and%20Delhi's%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20--%20to%20be%20called%20in%20for%20questioning%20ahead%20of%20the%20national%20elections%20due%20in%20summer.%20Mr%20Soren%20has%20now%20been%20arrested%20after%20repeated%20no-show.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20case%20involves%20alleged%20siphoning%20of%20funds%20belonging%20to%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Cricket%20Association%20or%20JKCA%2C%20which%20were%20apparently%20being%20transferred%20to%20personal%20bank%20accounts%20of%20various%20people%2C%20including%20the%20office%20bearers%20of%20the%20association.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnBetween%202001%20and%202012%2C%20the%20BCCI%20(Board%20of%20Cricket%20Control%2C%20India)%20had%20given%20Rs%20112%20crore%20to%20JKCA%20for%20the%20development%20of%20cricket%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20money%20laundering%20probe%20started%20in%202018%20after%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20filed%20a%20chargesheet%20against%20the%20office-bearers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Abdullah%2C%20who%20was%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20cricket%20association%20at%20the%20time%2C%20was%20chargesheeted%20by%20the%20Central%20agency%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chargesheet%20against%20him%20claims%20that%20during%20his%20tenure%20as%20the%20cricket%20association%20chief%2C%20Mr%20Abdullah%20diverted%20the%20funds%20received%20by%20the%20officials%20and%20others%20in%20the%20name%20of%20development%20of%20the%20game%20and%20used%20it%20for%20personal%20gains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20funds%20were%20first%20sent%20to%20many%20private%20bank%20accounts%20and%20were%20later%20divided%20among%20the%20accused%2C%20the%20chargesheet%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707748140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2Fjce4kuc_farooq-abdullah-1200_625x300_08_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffarooq-abdullah-summoned-by-central-probe-agency-tomorrow-for-questioning-over-alleged-money-laundering-5044403%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Farooq%20Abdullah%20summoned%20by%20central%20probe%20agency%20tomorrow%20for%20questioning%20over%20alleged%20money%20laundering%22%2