26quot%3B%20without%20the%20means%20to%20apply%20for%20job%20or%20ration%20cards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20MLA%20Kamalakhya%20Dey%20Purkayastha%20brought%20up%20the%20issue%20of%20%26quot%3BRam%20bhakts%26quot%3B%20unable%20to%20apply%20for%20Aadhaar%20since%20their%20biometrics%20are%20blocked%20till%20the%20NRC%20exercise%20is%20complete.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20NRC%20final%20draft%20was%20published%20on%20August%2031%2C%202019%20but%20many%20people%20were%20left%20out.%20Due%20to%20biometrics%20blocked%20for%20the%20pending%20NRC%2C%20they%20cannot%20apply%20for%20job%20and%20ration%20cards.%20The%20Ram%20bhakts%20have%20no%20Aadhaar%20cards%20and%20are%20facing%20problems.%20I%20request%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20when%20would%20the%20Ram%20bhakts%20get%20Aadhaar%3F%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Purkayastha%20said%20in%20the%20assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sarma%2C%20taking%20the%20question%20head-on%2C%20took%20a%20swipe%20at%20the%20Opposition%20in%20his%20reply%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20government%20has%20been%20doing%20certain%20things%20for%20Ram%20bhakts%2C%20but%20when%20we%20work%20to%20solve%20problems%2C%20some%20people%20sitting%20in%20front%20of%20us%20may%20create%20problems.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Supreme%20Court%20asked%20us%20to%20collect%2027%20lakh%20biometrics%2C%20and%20we%20have%20collected%20them.%20The%20whole%20data%20will%20be%20preserved%2C%20and%20people%20will%20get%20Aadhaar...%20We%20know%20the%20NRC%20was%20done%2C%20but%20the%20final%20process%20has%20not%20completed%20yet%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sarma%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Assam%20government%20in%20its%20budget%20has%20made%20a%20special%20allocation%20to%20take%2025%2C000%20devotees%20from%20the%20state%20to%20the%20new%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya.%20The%20budget%20also%20includes%20plays%20themed%20on%20Lord%20Ram%20for%20children%20in%20Assam.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707747540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%