d%20is%20oftened%20referred%20to%20as%20the%20'lungs%20of%20Bengaluru'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20proposal%2C%20which%20had%20been%20on%20hold%20for%20the%20past%20five%20years%20due%20to%20sustained%20opposition%20from%20activists%20and%20environmentalists%2C%20now%20faces%20renewed%20public%20scrutiny.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCubbon%20Park%20is%20not%20just%20a%20park%2C%20but%20an%20emotion%20for%20many%20of%20us%20who%20have%20been%20born%20and%20brought%20up%20in%20Bengaluru.%20With%20the%20kind%20of%20stressful%20lives%20we%20lead%2C%20Cubbon%20Park%20is%20where%20people%20of%20the%20city%20come%20with%20their%20friends%2C%20children%2C%20relatives%20to%20spend%20some%20quality%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20of%20the%20acitivists%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20just%20about%20constructing%20a%2010-storey%20building%20but%20also%20building%20a%20parking%20space%20for%20it%2C%20and%20the%20traffic%20that%20it%20will%20lead%20into%20the%20area.%20They%20are%20basically%20trying%20to%20kill%20this%20entire%20space.%20Bengaluru%20is%20a%20big%20city%2C%20why%20not%20move%20your%20project%20elsewhere%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Cubbon%20Park%20Walkers'%20Association%20also%20expressed%20opposition%20to%20a%20recent%20government%20order%20issued%20by%20the%20Horticulture%20Department%20on%20February%208.%20The%20order%20permits%20the%20movement%20of%20vehicles%20inside%20Cubbon%20Park%20on%20the%20second%20and%20fourth%20Saturdays%20for%20a%20period%20of%20three%20months%2C%20further%20fueling%20concerns%20about%20the%20park's%20ecological%20integrity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20compare%20Bengaluru%20with%20other%20metro%20cities%2C%20even%20with%20the%20kind%20of%20traffic%20that%20we%20have%2C%20our%20Air%20Quality%20Index%20(AQI)%20is%20better%20thanks%20to%20mini%20forests%20like%20Cubbon%20Park%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20another%20activist.%20%26quot%3BCubbon%20Park%20is%20considered%20to%20be%20the%20'lungs%20of%20the%20city'%2C%20so%20destroying%20it%20makes%20no%20sense.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmidst%20the%20growing%20opposition%2C%20prominent%20voices%2C%20including%20Kiran%20Mazumdar-Shaw%2C%20the%20Executive%20Chairperson%20of%20Biocon%20Ltd%2C%20have%20spoken%20out%20against%20the%20proposal.%20In%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20she%20expressed%20concern%20about%20the%20impact%20on%20Bengaluru's%20identity%20as%20the%20'Garden%20City%2C'%20urging%20the%20authorities%20to%20refrain%20from%20such%20%26quot%3Bharebrained%20proposals.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20are%20we%20destroying%20our%20Garden%20City%20with%20such%20harebrained%20proposals!%20%C2%A0Cubbon%20Park%20must%20be%20untouched.%20No%20construction%20should%20be%20permitted%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EWhy%20are%20we%20destroying%20our%20Garden%20City%20with%20such%20harebrained%20proposals!%20Cubbon%20Park%20must%20be%20untouched.%20No%20construction%20should%20be%20permitted%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FW2FW2JGzkl%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FW2FW2JGzkl%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Kiran%20Mazumdar-Shaw%20(%40kiranshaw)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkiranshaw%2Fstatus%2F1756590710881722546%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2011%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20leader%20and%20MP%20from%20Bangalore%20Central%2C%20PC%20Mohan%20went%20as%20far%20as%20to%20term%20the%20move%20as%20%26quot%3Bgreen%20genocide%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20Congress%20Govt's%20proposal%20to%20erect%20a%2010-storey%20annex%20in%20Cubbon%20Park%20is%20an%20assault%20on%20our%20city's%20greenery.%20Bengaluru's%20beloved%20lung%20space%20must%20be%20safeguarded%2C%20not%20suffocated%20by