o%2Ft-19016346%5C%22%3ENATO%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20had%20not%20met%20their%20financial%20obligations%2C%20in%20remarks%20that%20the%20White%20House%20rejected%20as%20%E2%80%9Cappalling%20and%20unhinged.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20a%20campaign%20rally%20in%20South%20Carolina%20Saturday%2C%20the%20Republican%20presidential%20nomination%20frontrunner%20appeared%20to%20recount%20a%20conversation%20with%20a%20fellow%20head%20of%20state%20at%20an%20unspecified%20NATO%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20presidents%20of%20a%20big%20country%20stood%20up%20and%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98Well%2C%20sir%2C%20if%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20pay%2C%20and%20we%E2%80%99re%20attacked%20by%20Russia%2C%20will%20you%20protect%20us%3F%E2%80%99%20I%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98You%20didn%E2%80%99t%20pay%2C%20you%E2%80%99re%20delinquent%3F'%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNo%2C%20I%20would%20not%20protect%20you.%20In%20fact%2C%20I%20would%20encourage%20them%20to%20do%20whatever%20the%20hell%20they%20want.%20You%20got%20to%20pay.%20You%20got%20to%20pay%20your%20bills.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NATO%20treaty%20contains%20a%20provision%20that%20assures%20mutual%20defense%20of%20member%20states%20if%20one%20is%20attacked%2C%20but%20it%20also%20stipulates%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fgermanys-defense-spending-balancing-nato-and-ukraine-aid%2Fa-68038674%5C%22%3Emembers%20should%C2%A0spend%202%25%20of%20their%20GDP%20on%20defense%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20target%20that%20the%20majority%20of%20states%20regularly%20fail%20to%20meet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBiden%20labels%20Trump%E2%80%99s%20remarks%20%E2%80%98appalling%20and%20dangerous%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20long%20expressed%20skepticism%20about%20the%2031-nation%20military%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20being%20asked%20about%20Trump%E2%80%99s%20statement%20White%20House%20spokesperson%20Andrew%20Bates%2C%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CEncouraging%20invasions%20of%20our%20closest%20allies%20by%20murderous%20regimes%20is%20appalling%20and%20unhinged%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20endangers%20American%20national%20security%2C%20global%20stability%20and%20our%20economy%20at%20home.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fjoe-biden%2Ft-55668302%5C%22%3EJoe%20Biden%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0criticized%C2%A0%E2%80%9Cappalling%20and%20dangerous%E2%80%9D%20comments%20by%20Trump.%C2%A0Biden%20said%C2%A0Sunday%20that%20the%20former%20president%20seeks%20to%20give%20Russian%20leader%20Vladimir%20Putin%20%E2%80%9Ca%20greenlight%20for%20more%20war%20and%20violence.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDonald%20Trump%E2%80%99s%20admission%20that%20he%20intends%20to%20give%20Putin%20a%20greenlight%20for%20more%20war%20and%20violence%2C%20to%20continue%20his%20brutal%20assault%20against%20a%20free%20Ukraine%2C%20and%20to%20expand%20his%20aggression%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Poland%20and%20the%20Baltic%20States%20are%20appalling%20and%20dangerous%2C%E2%80%9D%20Biden%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEuropean%20Council%20President%20Charles%20Michel%20also%20denounced%20Trump%E2%80%99s%C2%A0comments%20as%20%E2%80%9Creckless.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Transatlantic%20Alliance%20has%20underpinned%20the%20security%20and%20the%20prosperity%20of%20Americans%2C%20Canadians%20and%20Europeans%20for%2075%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Michel%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter.%E2%80%9D%20Reckless%20statements%20on%20%23NATO%E2%80%99s%20security%C2%A0and%20Art%205%20(Article%205)%20solidarity%20serve%20only%20Putin%E2%80%99s%20interest.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArticle%205%20of%20the%C2%A0%20949%20North%20Atlantic%20Treaty%20says%20that%20if%20a%20NATO%20Ally%20is%20attacked%2C%20each%C2%A0member%20of%20the%20Alliance%20will%20consider%20this%C2%A0an%C2%A0attack%20against%20all%20members%20and%20will%20take%20the%20actions%20it%20deems%20necessary%20to%20assist%20the%20ally%20under%20threat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENATO%20chief%20Jens%20Stoltenberg%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20warned%20in%20a%20statement%20that%2C%20%E2%80%9CAny%20suggestion%20that%20allies%20will%20not%20defend%20each%20other%20undermines%20all%20of%20our%20security%2C%20including%20that%20of%20the%20US.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAny%20attack%20on%20NATO%20will%20be%20met%20with%20a%20united%20and%20forceful%20response%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20looks%20set%20to%20run%20again%20as%20the%20Republican%20candidate%20for%20the%20White%20House%20in%20this%20year%E2%80%99s%20presidential%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%E2%80%99s%20comments%20came%20after%20Senate%20Republicans%20on%20Wednesday%20rejected%20a%20bipartisan%20bill%20that%20would%20have%20included%20crucially%20needed%20new%20funding%20for%20Ukraine%2C%20and%20aid%20for%20ally%20Israel%2C%20along%20with%20reforms%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20US-Mexico%20border%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Senate%20bill%E2%80%99s%20death%20highlighted%20Trump%E2%80%99s%20tight%20hold%20on%20the%20Republican%20Party%2C%20as%20its%20lawmakers%20acceded%20to%20the%20former%20president%E2%80%99s%20calls%20to%20shoot%20down%20any%20deal%20in%20order%20to%20deny%20Biden%20a%20win%20on%20immigration%20ahead%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fus-presidential-election-2024%2Ft-65733013%5C%22%3ENovember%E2%80%99s%20election%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrump%E2%80%99s%20relationship%20with%20NATO%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%202016%20presidential%20campaign%2C%20Trump%20shocked%20Western%20allies%20by%20cautioning%20that%20under%20his%20leadership%20the%20US%20might%20abandon%20its%20NATO%20treaty%20commitments%20and%20only%20come%20to%20the%20defense%20of%20those%20nations%20that%C2%A0meet%20the%20bloc%E2%80%99s%20military%20funding%20guidelines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20presidency%2C%20Trump%20eventually%20endorsed%20NATO%E2%80%99s%2