%20I%20convincingly%20disagree%20on%20factual%20and%20moral%20grounds.%20Me%20lending%20my%20voice%20to%20them%20could%20constitute%20a%20constitutional%20travesty%2C%20hence%20with%20respect%20to%20the%20House%2C%20I%20conclude%20my%20address.%20Wish%20this%20House%20a%20productive%20and%20healthy%20discussion%20for%20the%20good%20of%20the%20people.%20Vaazhga%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Vaazhaga%20Bharatam%2C%20Jai%20Hind%2C%20Jai%20Bharat%2C%20Nandri%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ravi%20added%2C%20as%20per%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fchennai%2Ftn-governor-ravi-dmk-regime-not-respecting-national-anthem-9156907%2F%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFurther%2C%20the%20governor%20alleged%20that%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Assembly%20had%20repeatedly%20ignored%20his%20request%20to%20play%20the%20national%20anthem%20before%20and%20after%20the%20address.%20He%20underlined%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Cshow%20due%20respect%20to%20the%20national%20anthem%E2%80%9D.%20As%20per%20%3Cem%3EThe%20News%20Minute%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Ftamil-nadu%2Ftn-guv-rn-ravi-refuses-to-read-customary-speech-in-assembly-on-moral-grounds%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20is%20a%20custom%20in%20the%20southern%20state%20to%20sing%20t%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehe%20%E2%80%98Tamil%20Thai%20Vazhthu%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20song%20of%20praise%20to%20the%20Tamil%20language%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20Assembly%20sessions%20and%20end%20the%20session%20with%20national%20anthem.%20%C2%A0While%20Ravi%20refused%20to%20continue%20reading%20the%20c%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eustomary%20address%C2%A0prepared%20for%20him%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ETamil%20Nadu%20assembly%20Speaker%20M.%20Appavu%20read%20out%20the%20Tamil%20version%20of%20the%20speech.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%3C%