ses%20since%20Sunday%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20farmers%20said%20that%20they%20are%20committed%20to%20getting%20their%20demands%20fulfilled%2C%20which%20were%20promised%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20after%20they%20had%20lifted%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20in%20November%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20Amritsar%20in%20Punjab%20to%20Ambala%2C%20Kurukshetra%20in%20Haryana%2C%20all%20that%20meets%20the%20eye%20on%20the%20highway%20or%20in%20the%20villages%20were%20farmers%20loading%20their%20tractors%20with%20ration%2C%20tents%2C%20beds%2C%20wood%20and%20other%20essentials%20and%20moving%20to%20Delhi.%20Considering%20the%20466-km-long%20journey%2C%20farmers%20started%20from%20Amritsar%20on%20February%2012%20after%20conducting%20prayers%20at%20Akal%20Takth%20in%20Golden%20Temple%2C%20Amritsar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20call%20for%20the%20protest%20has%20been%20given%20by%20Sanyukt%20Kisan%20Morcha%20(non-political)%20and%20the%20newly%20launched%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Morcha%20(KMM)%20led%20by%20senior%20farmer%20union%20leaders%20Jagjeet%20Singh%20Dallewal%20and%20Sarvan%20Singh%20Pandher.%20The%20larger%20umbrella%20group%20which%20organised%20the%202020%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20%E2%80%93%20Samyukt%20Kisan%20Morcha%20%E2%80%93%20has%20said%20it%20is%20not%20participating%20in%20these%20protests%2C%20and%20is%20organising%20a%20different%20agitation%20on%20February%2016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20farmers%20are%20moving%20to%20Delhi%2C%20the%20Haryana%20government%20has%20constructed%20a%2012-layer%20blockage%20on%20the%20Punjab-Haryana%20border%20highway%20situated%20on%20river%20Ghaggar.%20The%20Haryana%20police%20has%20constructed%20cemented%20walls%2C%20put%20up%20barricades%20covered%20in%20long%20concertina%20wires%2C%20dug%20iron%20nails%20into%20concrete%20to%20deflate%20the%20tires%20of%20the%20tractors%2C%20and%20filled%20the%20intersections%20between%20cemented%20barricades%20with%20gravel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20if%20this%20were%20not%20enough%2C%20they%20also%20dug%20up%20the%20Ghaggar%20riverbed%2C%20so%20that%20the%20farmers%20could%20not%20cross%20over%20to%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20Haryana%20border.%20The%20Haryana%20police%20also%20conducted%20a%20mock%20drill%20by%20using%20teargas%20on%20the%20highway%20and%20randomly%20checking%20commuters%E2%80%99%20Aadhar%20cards%20for%20identity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20reports%2C%20Haryana%20police%20teams%20were%20also%20going%20to%20villages%20to%20track%20farmers%E2%80%99%20movements%20and%20conducting%20raids%20at%20their%20houses.%20Evading%20police%20raids%20and%20harassment%2C%20many%20Haryana-based%20farmer%20union%20leaders%20have%20been%20staying%20in%20Punjab%20for%20the%20past%20few%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Haryana%20government%20has%20also%20reportedly%20turned%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fharyana-converts-2-stadiums-into-temporary-jails-ahead-of-farmers-march-to-delhi-5038447%5C%22%3Etwo%20large%20stadiums%20into%20temporary%20jails%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20case%20people%20need%20to%20be%20detained%20in%20large%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F12170422%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-12-at-3.12.24-PM-1.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F12170422%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-12-at-3.12.24-PM-1.jpeg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F12170422%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-12-at-3.12.24-PM-1-300x183.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F12170422%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-12-at-3.12.24-PM-1-1024x624.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-696