ns%20that%20the%20farmers%20were%20instigated%20by%20opposition%20leaders%20to%20conduct%20the%20protest%2C%20Manjit%20Singh%20Rai%20said%20farmers%20were%20raising%20their%20voice%20for%20themselves.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20been%20left%20on%20our%20own%20to%20fight%20for%20our%20rights.%20How%20did%20the%20opposition%20come%20into%20this%20picture%3F%20Our%20question%20is%20that%20if%20the%20Modi%20government%20can%20waive%20off%20the%20loans%20of%20corporate%20houses%2C%20then%20why%20can%E2%80%99t%20they%20do%20away%20with%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20loans%3F%20The%20Modi%20government%20should%20remember%20that%20farmers%20across%20the%20world%20were%20uniting%20against%20the%20corporate%20houses%20and%20everywhere%20the%20governments%20had%20to%20bow%20before%20the%20people%E2%80%99s%20voice.%20Look%20how%20Europe%E2%80%99s%20farmers%20were%20on%20the%20roads%20after%20taking%20inspiration%20from%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20last%20time%20too%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20had%20apologised%20to%20the%20farmers%20for%20passing%20the%20three%20farm%20laws%2C%20and%20this%20time%20also%20they%20will%20apologise%20to%20the%20farmers%20for%20not%20fulfilling%20their%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20on%20Sunday%2C%20Punjab%20chief%20minister%20Bhagwant%20Mann%20had%20also%20cornered%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20asked%20them%20not%20to%20create%20another%20border%20between%20Punjab%20and%20India.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20as%20many%20barbed%20wires%20placed%20from%20Haryana%20to%20Delhi%20as%20there%20are%20at%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20border%20with%20Pakistan.%20The%20Union%20government%20should%20accept%20the%20legitimate%20demands%20of%20the%20farmers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20Tarn%20Taran%20district%20near%20Amritsar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2