hat%20the%20atmosphere%20of%20political%20instability%20currently%20being%20created%20in%20the%20country%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20polls%20is%20also%20posing%20a%20threat%20to%20the%20security%20and%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20of%20the%20country.%20Therefore%2C%20there%20is%20a%20need%20for%20all%20stakeholders%20including%20the%20political%20leadership%20to%20come%20together%20and%20decide%20on%20a%20concrete%20strategy%20to%20stabilise%20the%20elected%20assembly.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20some%20of%20its%20analyses%2C%20the%20election%20results%20have%20been%20described%20as%20sympathy%20for%20Imran%20Khan%20and%20public%20anger.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20newspaper%20also%20jibed%20at%20the%20current%20results%20and%20the%20discrepancies%20in%20them%20saying%20that%20it%20seemed%20to%20be%20the%20work%20of%20%E2%80%98secret%20angels%E2%80%99%20who%20cast%20their%20votes.%20These%20%E2%80%98angels%E2%80%99%20also%20took%20away%20votes%2C%20when%20convenient%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20democratic%20protocol%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EDaily%20Ausaf%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20also%20questioned%20the%20Election%20Commission%20and%20wrote%20that%20it%20is%20the%20responsibility%20of%20the%20political%20parties%20to%20accept%20their%20respective%20situations%20instead%20of%20forming%20a%20government%20through%20horse%20trading.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20its%20analyses%20stated%20that%20these%20results%20will%20perhaps%20open%20the%20eyes%20of%20the%20establishment.%20It%20espoused%20a%20democratic%20way%20and%20discouraged%20the%20buying%20out%20of%20independent%20candidates.%20If%20this%20happens%2C%20it%20will%20be%20no%20less%20than%20a%20political%20revolution.%20With%20this%2C%20the%20previous%20blot%20of%20interference%20in%20politics%20by%20the%20establishment%2C%20that%20is%2C%20the%20Pakistani%20Army%20wi