red%20only%20male%20officers%20for%20permanent%20commission%20and%20women%20were%20excluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20the%20principal%20grievance%20of%20the%20women%20SSCOs%20was%20that%20by%20denying%20them%20permanent%20commission%20%E2%80%93%20which%20carries%20with%20it%20certain%20privileges%20of%20rank%20including%20pension%20%E2%80%93%20they%20had%20been%20subjected%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F168731%2Fgender-equality-women-empowerment-jamnalal-bajaj-awards%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egender%20discrimination%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGarima%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20short%20service%20commission%20officer%20will%20only%20be%20given%2010%20years%20in%20service%20and%20an%20extension%20of%20four%20years%20maximum.%20So%2C%20female%20officers%20did%20not%20serve%20beyond%2014%20years%20and%20didn%E2%80%99t%20reach%20the%20age%20of%20retirement.%20Whereas%20a%20permanent%20commission%20officer%20will%20serve%20for%20about%2030-35%20years%2C%20or%20more%20depending%20on%20the%20rank.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20opportunity%20was%20not%20given%20to%20women%20officers.%20We%E2%80%99ve%20been%20as%20good%20as%20men%20in%20uniform%2C%20or%20maybe%20better%2C%20then%20why%20were%20we%20not%20given%20permanent%20commission%3F%E2%80%9D%20she%20asks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-Sachdeva-5-1707395429.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20principal%20grievance%20of%20the%20women%20officers%20was%20that%20by%20denying%20them%20a%20permanent%20commission%2C%20they%20were%20subjected%20to%20gender%20discrimination.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-Sachdeva-5-1707395429.jpg%