0away.%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20IAF%20and%20serve%20for%20more%20years%2C%20just%20like%20my%20male%20counterparts%2C%20but%20we%20weren%E2%80%99t%20allowed%20to%20do%20so%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds%20with%20a%20sigh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20raise%20this%20issue%2C%2032%20female%20officers%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20court%20and%20in%202003%2C%20a%20Public%20Interest%20Litigation%20(PIL)%20was%20instituted%20before%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20titled%20%E2%80%98Babita%20Puniya%20for%20the%20grant%20of%20permanent%20commission%20to%20women%20SSC%20Officers%E2%80%99%2C%20highlighting%20the%20gender%20discrimination%20being%20meted%20out%20to%20women%20officers%20in%20the%20armed%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAfter%20years%20of%20struggle%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202010%2C%20the%20High%20Court%20stated%20that%20the%20Permanent%20Commission%20shall%20be%20offered%20to%20women%20officers%20after%20the%20completion%20of%20five%20years%2C%20subject%20to%20vacancies%20and%20suitability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20judgment%20was%20said%20to%20be%20implemented%20by%20the%20IAF%20for%20only%20those%20officers%20who%20were%20in%20service%20or%20those%20retired%2Freleased%20officers%20who%20were%20not%20in%20service%20as%20on%2012%20March%202010%20but%20had%20filed%20writ%20petitions%20before%20their%20release%20%E2%80%93%20a%20criterion%20that%20did%20not%20match%20with%20the%20appellants%20and%20hence%20they%20were%20left%20out%20from%20the%20reinstatement%20plan%20of%20the%20IAF.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-1707458172.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%202022%2C%20as%20many%20as%2032%20women%20officers%20of%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20won%20a%2012-year-long%20legal%20battle%20against%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-1707458172.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-1707458172-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-1707458172-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-1707458172-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-1707458172-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-341232%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIn%202022%2C%20as%20many%20as%2032%20women%20officers%20of%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20won%20a%2012-year-long%20legal%20battle%20against%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20immediately%20approached%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20challenging%20the%20manner%20of%20implementation%20of%20the%20decision%20in%20Babita%20Puniya%E2%80%99s%20case%20by%20the%20IAF.%20However%2C%20by%20an%20order%20dated%2027%20September%202011%2C%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20dismissed%20the%20review%20petitions%20filed%20against%20the%20impugned%20judgment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20these%20officers%20joined%20the%20service%20between%201993%20and%201998%20and%20were%20eventually%20released%20from%20service%20between%20December%202006%20and%202009.%20As%20these%20female%20officers%20put%20in%20long%20years%20of%20service%20for%20the%20IAF%2C%20the%20lawyers%20were%20of%20the%20view%20that%20they%20should%20be%20considered%20for%20the%20grant%20of%20pensionary%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThanks%20to%20the%20team%20of%20lawyers%2C%20including%20Garima%20Sachdeva%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%202022%20directed%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F70596%2Ffirst-