.%20We%20fought%20our%20battle%20up%20to%20the%20highest%20court%20of%20justice%20and%20won%20against%20IAF.%20The%20decision%20has%20given%20me%20mental%20peace.%20Now%2C%20I%20await%20my%20pensionary%20benefits%20that%20are%20in%20the%20process.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGarima%20opines%20that%20these%2032%20women%20have%20set%20a%20benchmark%20for%20other%20female%20officers.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20unfortunate%20that%20the%20matter%20went%20on%20for%20such%20a%20long%20time.%20It%20was%20heartbreaking%20to%20see%20how%20these%20women%20officers%20who%20fought%20for%20so%20long%20didn%E2%80%99t%20really%20get%20any%20tangible%20satisfaction%20out%20of%20it.%20The%20only%20satisfaction%20was%20that%20they%20won%20and%20they%20set%20up%20a%20benchmark%20for%20all%20the%20coming%20generations%20ahead%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Garima%2C%20the%20court%20order%20gave%20her%20an%20immense%20sense%20of%20pride%20and%20strength.%20%E2%80%9CComing%20from%20an%20Air%20Force%20background%2C%20I%20had%20my%20heart%20and%20soul%20in%20this%20matter.%20I%20was%20happy%20that%20I%20could%20get%20the%20best%20out%20of%20my%20capabilities%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20think%20nothing%20beats%20the%20satisfaction%20that%20comes%20out%20of%20fighting%20for%20women%20in%20the%20male-dominated%20systems%20and%20emerging%20victorious%20for%20those%20who%20have%20high%20hopes%20in%20you%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Garima%2C%20who%20was%20recently%20appointed%20as%20a%20Senior%20Panel%20Counsel%20at%20both%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20and%20the%20Principal%20Bench%20of%20Armed%20Forces%20Tribunal.%20She%20currently%20represents%20the%20armed%20forces%20before%20these%20forums.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Garima%20Sachdeva)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707460807000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-Sachdeva-1