thebetterindia.com%2F339578%2Fradhika-gupta-shark-tank-india-judge-edelweiss-asset-management-broken-neck-ceo%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworking%20mother.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeciding%20whether%20to%20pursue%20a%20career%20or%20stay%20at%20home%2C%20contemplating%20parenthood%2C%20and%20considering%20how%20it%20might%20impact%20one%E2%80%99s%20professional%20trajectory%20are%20dilemmas%20faced%20by%20women%20of%20all%20ages%20and%20backgrounds.%20These%20questions%20are%20not%20exclusive%20to%20any%20particular%20demographic%3B%20they%20resonate%20across%20various%20roles%20and%20positions%20within%20organisations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20individuals%20in%20top%20leadership%20positions%2C%20such%20as%20Radhika%20Gupta%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Managing%20Director%20and%20CEO%20of%20Edelweiss%20Asset%20Management%20Limited%20%E2%80%94%20grapple%20with%20these%20uncertainties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERadhika%2C%20who%20is%20a%20mother%20to%20a%2019-month-old%20boy%2C%20has%20been%20outspoken%20about%20these%20issues%20and%20advocates%20for%20women%20to%20voice%20their%20concerns%20in%20the%20workplace.%20As%20the%20only%20female%20CEO%20among%20asset%20management%20companies%20in%20India%2C%20she%20embarked%20on%20motherhood%20at%20the%20age%20of%2039%2C%20grappling%20with%20concerns%20about%20balancing%20work%20and%20life%20responsibilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20her%20thoughts%20on%20a%20podcast%20%E2%80%98The%20BarberShop%20with%20Shantanu%E2%80%99%2C%20she%20mentioned%20that%20she%20%E2%80%9Cdesperately%20Googled%20examples%20of%20Indian%20CEOs%20who%20were%20pregnant%2C%20but%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20find%20a%20single%20example%20as%20most%20women%20have%20had%20kids%20earlier%E2%80%9D.%20She%20found%20the%20story%20of%20former%20Yahoo%20CEO%20Marissa%20Mayer%2C%20which%20gave%20her%20confidence%20and%20hope%20that%20%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20if%20she%20can%20do%20it%2C%20I%20can%20do%20it%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20spark%20dialogues%20around